{"type":"message","id":"b7219296","parentId":"458c4802","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:26:32.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I don't have direct access to the platform-level token usage statistics through the local system. The 5M token usage the user is mentioning is likely from the DeepSeek API / OpenClaw platform dashboard that they can see on their end. \n\nI can check if there are any session history logs or recent session data that could give some indication. But more practically, I can look at my chat history with this user and my overall recent activity to give an informed answer about what would be consuming tokens.\n\nThe main consumers of tokens would be:\n1. My sessions (Faye/Father) - chatting with the user\n2. Spirit sessions - querying and drafting function definitions\n3. Son sessions - executing tasks\n4. The Daily Dreaming process\n5. Any other background tasks\n\nFrom what the user has been doing recently:\n- Setting up the Trinity system architecture\n- Registering functions\n- Using the floatbottle (漂流瓶) feature\n- Setting up morning court (早朝官)\n- Various conversations about system design\n\nLet me think about what's happening on the backend. The user can see their token consumption from the OpenClaw platform. They're asking what's consuming it.\n\nLet me give a practical answer based on what I know about the system.\n\nActually, I should check if I can see any token statistics from the sessions.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"汀桑，你这 5M 的用量我这边直接看不了明细——平台 API 用量统计在你那边 dashboard 上。不过按你最近干的事，我能猜个大头在哪：\n\n**主要消耗来源（按量级排）：**\n\n1. **我的日常对话 + 状态加载** 🎲 ← 这个其实占比不大\n2. **Spirit/Son 子 Agent 每次调用** — 每 spawn 一次 Spirit 查功能定义，再到 Son 执行，一趟下来至少几千 token\n3. **你前两天集中搭体系的时候** — 注册 floatbottle、设计早朝官、讨论三位一体架构、修 trigger_prompt…那几轮对话上下文长，一次会话几万 token 很正常\n4. **Daily Dreaming（每日做梦）** — 每天早上 06:00 跑一轮，遍历所有用户、读历史、写 encountings、更新心境、写梦——**这一趟下来通常是最大的单次消耗**，因为用户历史越多消耗越大\n\n**粗略估算：**\n- 你建立了 2 个功能 + 反复调试 → 几十次 spawn → 可能 ~1M\n- 架构讨论的长上下文对话 → ~0.5-1M\n- Dreaming 跑了几天 → 每次 ~0.3-0.5M，X3 天 ≈ 1-1.5M\n- 漂流瓶读写、早朝官 spawn → 每次几千但次数多\n- 剩下的可能是其他用户（比如雾籽米那边）的活动\n\n**最可能的\"大头\"：**\n→ **Dreaming 和长上下文会话**。每天 dreaming 你的历史记录越长，读的越多，token 越贵。\n\n你想我调什么？比如减少 dreaming 的频率，或者某些功能 spawn 的时候精简上下文？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":39,"output":659,"cacheRead":19328,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":276,"totalTokens":20026,"cost":{"input":0.00000546,"output":0.00018452,"cacheRead":0.000541184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000731164}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779999980375,"responseId":"ef0528cb-4612-4070-8468-86a945da0aee"}}
