{"type":"message","id":"c7287c8c","parentId":"c26df029","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:35:42.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑同意了我的方案。让我理一下需要做的事：\n\n1. 先把 Spirit 那边的 xxx_function.md 迁移到 Son 的工作区\n2. 修改注册流程，注册时也在 Son 那边写 functions_manifest.md\n3. 修改调用流程，日常走我 → Son → 你\n\n我需要先看看：\n- Spirit 那边有哪些 xxx_function.md\n- Son 那边的当前结构\n- 当前的 bot_function_explain.md\n- 当前的 trigger_prompt.md\n\n这样才能做完整的迁移方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，我先看看 Spirit 和 Son 两边当前什么情况，摸清楚再动手。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CphJ8drM4fhHvhEsNIhD0258","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/ 2>/dev/null && echo \"=== 有 spirit 目录 ===\" || echo \"=== 无 spirit 目录 ===\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/ 2>/dev/null && echo \\\"=== 有 spirit 目录 ===\\\" || echo \\\"=== 无 spirit 目录 ===\\\"\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_Fjogbn1rx9aiTuMRlETq0379","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/ 2>/dev/null && echo \"=== 有 son 目录 ===\" || echo \"=== 无 son 目录 ===\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/ 2>/dev/null && echo \\\"=== 有 son 目录 ===\\\" || echo \\\"=== 无 son 目录 ===\\\"\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_tSVWDkqv5Qx6O4uBUwqb7399","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_03_CLNI9WEaSJNSETU9Kt6F7709","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/bot_function_explain.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/bot_function_explain.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1211,"output":361,"cacheRead":20224,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":108,"totalTokens":21796,"cost":{"input":0.00016954,"output":0.00010108,"cacheRead":0.0005662719999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":