{"type":"message","id":"f66731ee","parentId":"246ef572","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:36:16.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now update Father's trigger_prompt.md — change all `→ Spirit → Son` to just `→ Son`.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在改我的 trigger_prompt.md，日常使用直接 → Son："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_SAcddJlbfjQzIzzvfgkO3923","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":917,"output":95,"cacheRead":32000,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":25,"totalTokens":33012,"cost":{"input":0.00012838000000000001,"output":0.000026600000000000003,"cacheRead":0.000896,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00105098}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780000575088,"responseId":"c189bf7d-93e6-4113-ab70-3b88ce702418"}}
{"type":"message","id":"74724a6c","parentId":"f66731ee","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:36:17.180Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_SAcddJlbfjQzIzzvfgkO3923","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\n\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\n> \n> 匹配原则：\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\"扔个瓶子\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\n> - 只有命中表中触发语时才走 Spirit → Son 流程\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\n\n---\n\n## 已注册触发词\n\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 |\n|--------|---------|---------|\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) |\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 |\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md |\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/存照片` `存照片` `/看相册` `看相册` `/看照片` `看照片` `/搜照片` `搜照片` `/删照片` `删照片` | 相册笔记 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780000577179}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6347654","parentId":"74724a6c","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:36:23.393Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ET_1tVYMlWqAFQbhQG8dUzT0520","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md","content":"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\n\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\n> \n> 匹配原则：\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\"扔个瓶子\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\n> - 命中表中触发语时直接 spawn Son，传 {function, action, params} 指令\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\n> \n> **不再绕 Spirit。** 功能定义已迁移到 Son 的工作区，日常使用 Father → Son 直达。\n\n---\n\n## 已注册触发词\n\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 | Son 指令 |\n|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) | — |\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 | — |\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md → Father → Son(同步功能定义) | — |\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:throw, params:{content}}` |\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:pickup}` |\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:list}` |\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:reply, params:{id, content}}` |\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | → Son | `{function:memo, action:create/list/update/toggle/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | → Son | `{function:morningcourt, action:manual/set/disable, params:{...}}` |\n| `/存照片` `存照片` `/看相册` `看相册` `/看照片` `看照片` `/搜照片` `搜照片` `/删照片` `删照片` | 相册笔记 | → Son | `{function:album, action:save/list/view/search/delete, params:{...}}` |\n"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\", \"content\": \"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\\n\\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\\n> \\n> 匹配原则：\\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\\\"扔个瓶子\\\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\\n> - 命中表中触发语时直接 spawn Son，传 {function, action, params} 指令\\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\\n> \\n> **不再绕 Spirit。** 功能定义已迁移到 Son 的工作区，日常使用 Father → Son 直达。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 已注册触发词\\n\\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 | Son 指令 |\\n|--------|---------|---------|----------|\\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) | — |\\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 | — |\\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md → Father → Son(同步功能定义) | — |\\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:throw, params:{content}}` |\\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:pickup}` |\\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:list}` |\\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:reply, params:{id, content}}` |\\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | → Son | `{function:memo, action:create/list/update/toggle/delete, params:{...}}` |\\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | → Son | `{function:morningcourt, action:manual/set/disable, params:{...}}` |\\n| `/存照片` `存照片` `/看相册` `看相册` `/看照片` `看照片` `/搜照片` `搜照片` `/删照片` `删照片` | 相册笔记 | → Son | `{function:album, action:save/list/view/search/delete, params:{...}}` |\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":574,"output":684,"cacheRead":32896,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":34154,"cost":{"input":0.00008036000000000001,"output":0.00019152,"cacheRead":0.000921088,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001192968}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780000577203,"responseId":"39f2db4b-22fd-461c-84b9-116c616cd565"}}
