{"type":"message","id":"978feb87","parentId":"f5e07e0b","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:36:48.677Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ET_PB5jHtZAs3XxSasXB7IB0532","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"```bash\n# 喊 Spirit（查功能/注册/删除）\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"spirit\",\n  task: \"汀桑说/扔瓶子 今天天气真好。翻一下 floatbottle 的定义，给 Son 组好指令扔过来。\",\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 喊 Son（干活）\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  task: \"把这段话存成新瓶子：内容'今天天气真好'，sender 留汀桑的 ID。\",\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n```\n\n派完活等结果用 `sessions_yield`，拿到了直接转给用户。","newText":"```bash\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"floatbottle\",\"action\":\"throw\",\"params\":{\"content\":\"今天天气真好\"},\"sender_id\":\"汀桑的ID\"}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"spirit\",\n  task: \"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\",\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n```\n\n派完活等结果用 `sessions_yield`，拿到了直接转给用户。"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"```bash\\n# 喊 Spirit（查功能/注册/删除）\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"spirit\\\",\\n  task: \\\"汀桑说/扔瓶子 今天天气真好。翻一下 floatbottle 的定义，给 Son 组好指令扔过来。\\\",\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# 喊 Son（干活）\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"son\\\",\\n  task: \\\"把这段话存成新瓶子：内容'今天天气真好'，sender 留汀桑的 ID。\\\",\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n```\\n\\n派完活等结果用 `sessions_yield`，拿到了直接转给用户。\",\"newText\":\"```bash\\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"son\\\",\\n  task: '{\\\"function\\\":\\\"floatbottle\\\",\\\"action\\\":\\\"throw\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\"今天天气真好\\\"},\\\"sender_id\\\":\\\"汀桑的ID\\\"}',\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"spirit\\\",\\n  task: \\\"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\\\",\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n```\\n\\