{"type":"message","id":"aeea1e4f","parentId":"5769014d","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:39:37.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the latest Son subagent session (the memo lookup):\n\n```\n\"totalTokens\": 10907\n```\n\nWait, that's interesting - it's 10907 tokens input, 29 output. And looking at the model, it's using qwen-vl-max-latest for Son, not DeepSeek.\n\nSo for this memo lookup call:\n- Father (me): This session shows 39k input / 193 output (but this includes the whole conversation, not just this call)\n- Son subagent: 10,907 input tokens + 29 output tokens = ~10,936 total\n\nBut the key comparison would be:\n- **Old flow** (if Spirit was involved): Son would still use ~10-11k, PLUS Spirit would need its own ~8-12k for reading function definitions and routing. So total per call: ~20-25k tokens.\n- **New flow**: Son alone at ~10.9k total. No Spirit overhead.\n\nSo we saved about 8-12k tokens per call by cutting out Spirit. For simple operations like memo list, it's a solid saving. For more complex operations the saving would be even bigger since Spirit's context would be larger.\n\nLet me give this to the user in a straightforward way.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这次 `/看备忘录` 的 token 账单：\n\n| 谁 | Input | Output | 总计 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **Son（子Agent）** | 10,907 | 29 | **~10,936** |\n| **我（Father）** | 算在会话整体里，分摊很小 | | |\n\n**跟改之前的对比：**\n\n改之前同样这么一条 `/看备忘录`，流程是：\n1. 我 spawn Spirit → Spirit 读 bot_function_explain.md + memo_function.md → 组指令 → **~8-12k tokens**\n2. 再 spawn Son → 再读一遍 memo_function.md → 执行 → **~10-11k tokens**\n\n**合计每趟 ~18-23k。**\n\n现在 → **直接 Son 一趟 ~10.9k**，省了一半。\n\n按你之前 5M 的用量来算，如果一半是日常功能调用的话，改了之后大概能省 **1-1.5M tokens/月**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":11345,"output":473,"cacheRead":43392,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":261,"totalTokens":55210,"cost":{"input":0.0015883000000000002,"output":0.00013244,"cacheRead":0.001214976,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002935716}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780000769784,"responseId":"0f6f6417-be5d-4245-b8da-c82265bc332b"}}
