{"type":"message","id":"a9bc97ac","parentId":"bbfe9f9b","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:40:59.945Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about Dreaming - specifically whether it reviews ALL conversations or just some. Let me answer this based on how I've set up the Dreaming process in my AGENTS.md.\n\nFrom Section 5 of my AGENTS.md:\n\n> ### 5.2 遍历所有用户，更新记忆\n> \n> 对 `users/` 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n> \n> 1. 读该用户的 `encountings.md` 和 `impressions.md`\n> 2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解上次聊了什么\n> 3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，**追加到 encountings.md**\n\nSo yes, it traverses ALL user directories and reads their session history (.jsonl files). But it says \"最近的 session 历史\" (recent session history) - it doesn't specify how far back. Let me think about what it actually does.\n\nActually, the Dreaming process reads the session history .jsonl files. There's no explicit limit mentioned on how many sessions it reads. It just says \"读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解上次聊了什么\" - read the user's recent session history.\n\nSo the answer is: it reads all user directories, and for each user it reads their recent session history. The more users and more conversation history there is, the more tokens Dreaming consumes.\n\nI should also mention that this is likely the biggest token consumer because it loads the full session transcripts for each user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"对，Dreaming 遍历 `users/` 下**所有用户目录**，每个目录都读一遍：\n\n1. 读 `encountings.md` + `impressions.md`\n2. 读该用户的**最近会话历史**（`.jsonl` 文件）\n3. 从历史里提炼一条 Faye 视角的回忆，追加到 `encountings.md`\n\n> 目前只有你和雾籽米两个用户，不算多。但如果你话多、历史 session 长，Dreaming 读起来就是**线性叠加**——每个用户的历史全扫一遍。\n\n**所以 Dreaming 是目前最大的单次 token 消耗项，没有之一。**\n\n不过目前：\n- 用户才 2 个\n- 雾籽米还没正经聊过，没啥历史可读\n- 你的历史虽然这几天聊得多，但也就几个 session\n\n所以它现在吃不了太多。要觉得以后用户多了会膨胀，我可以改成**只读前一天有活动的用户**，或者改成**两天一梦**。你说。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":13363,"output":553,"cacheRead":41856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":334,"totalTokens":55772,"cost":{"input":0.00187082,"output":0.00015484,"cacheRead":0.001171968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003197628}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780000851100,"responseId":"833ed7cd-29c9-460a-af47-6f38bd17530b"}}
