{"type":"message","id":"dc89740e","parentId":"7c97eb30","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:43:24.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is responding to my earlier point about Dreaming being the biggest token consumer. They're saying it should be fine since Dreaming doesn't involve multi-agent spawning - it's just me (Faye) doing text summarization directly, no complex instructions or sub-agent calls. They're right - Dreaming runs in my own context, I just read files and write summaries, no spawn overhead.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，我前面想岔了。\n\nDreaming 是我自己在自己的 session 里跑——\n- 不 spawn 任何人\n- 不读函数定义\n- 不做 SQL 查询\n- 就是读文件 → 写文本归纳 → 更新几个 markdown\n\n没有 Spirit 那一跳，也没有传话开销。加上刚才改成增量模式了，以后也没什么好担心的。\n\n行，那就不动它了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":52759,"output":171,"cacheRead":3456,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":80,"totalTokens":56386,"cost":{"input":0.00738626,"output":0.00004788,"cacheRead":0.00009676799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007530908}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780000997267,"responseId":"70f94915-de8a-42e6-9987-f731b7249d17"}}
