{"type":"message","id":"4c8a5b63","parentId":"f1f162bc","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:44:06.210Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to estimate how many tokens the Dreaming process would consume. Let me think about this based on the actual process described in AGENTS.md now.\n\nThe dreaming process for me (Faye/Father) is:\n\n1. **回顾自己** - Read a few small files (background.md, identity.md, state.md, dreams.md) - these are tiny markdown files, maybe 1-2k tokens total\n\n2. **遍历前一天有活动的用户** - Currently only 汀桑 has activity. Let me estimate:\n   - Read encountings.md + impressions.md - small files, maybe 1-2k total\n   - Read only yesterday's session history from the .jsonl file - this is the bigger part\n   - For 汀桑, yesterday's sessions: Let me look at the session history. From the sessions_list output earlier, there were Son subagent sessions. But the Father session itself - the conversation today has been extensive. The .jsonl files for the session would contain all the messages.\n\n   - Actually, the Father session transcript for yesterday would have the whole conversation history. Looking at the current conversation, it's been quite long - we've had a long discussion about token optimization, migrating functions, etc.\n\n   Let me estimate:\n   - My own context loading (background.md, identity.md, state.md, dreams.md): ~2-3k tokens\n   - Reading users/{sender_id}/encountings.md + impressions.md: ~1-2k tokens\n   - Reading yesterday's session transcript (.jsonl): this is the biggest variable. A full day of conversation could be 10-50k tokens depending on how much was talked about.\n   - Writing encountings.md entry + updating impressions.md: output maybe 300-500 tokens\n   - Updating state.md (heart indicators, relationship temperature): output ~200-300 tokens\n   - Writing a dream in dreams.md: output ~200-500 tokens\n\n   So total for a day with active users:\n   - Input: ~20-50k (mostly the session transcript reading)\n   - Output: ~1-2k\n   - Total: ~21-52k\n\nFor the current state with just 2 users but only 1 active:\n- Total ~20-30k tokens per dreaming run\n\nThat's quite reasonable actually. Even with 10 active users, if each has a typical day's conversation, maybe 50-200k tokens total depending on length.\n\nThe user is asking for an estimate, so let me give them a rough number based on what I can see.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"以目前的情况算一笔：\n\n**我（Faye）自己跑 Dreaming：**\n\n| 项目 | 大概 token |\n|---|---|\n| 读 heart/* 自己的文件（4个小的） | ~2k |\n| 读汀桑的 encountings + impressions | ~1k |\n| **读昨天汀桑的 session 历史** | **~15-30k**（看你昨天聊了多少） |\n| 写一条 encountings 记录 | ~0.5k |\n| 更新 state.md（心境+关系温度） | ~0.5k |\n| 写一条梦 | ~0.5k |\n| **总计** | **~20-35k 一趟** |\n\n现在只有你一个活跃用户，一天一次 Dreaming 大概 **2-3 万 token**。就算以后 10 个活跃用户，按平均每人每天聊 10-20k 来算，也就是 **100-200k 一趟**——对 5M 的量来说不算大头。\n\n**所以确实还好。** 你之前 5M 的主要消耗应该还是：\n- 早期注册功能时 Spirit 反复跑 + 文件读写\n- 长上下文架构讨论那一轮会话\n- 还有 Son 那边用的是 **qwen-vl-max-latest**（带视觉模型），图片处理本身就很吃 token\n\n等改完之后稳定用一段时间再看看账单，应该会明显降下来。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6266,"output":838,"cacheRead":50048,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":537,"totalTokens":57152,"cost":{"input":0.00087724,"output":0.00023464000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001401344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025132239999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780001032741,"responseId":"a2ae91d0-586d-4ed9-b91b-a88e1103baa3"}}
