{"type":"message","id":"1789491d","parentId":"a3f0e435","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:47:06.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit returned the menu. Let me forward this to the user. The stats show this Spirit call used 5.4k input + 588 output = ~6k tokens. This is the `/菜单` command which does need Spirit (it's a system-level query), so this is fine.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"📋 **已注册功能（共 4 个）**\n\n**1. 🍾 漂流瓶 (floatbottle)**\n`/扔瓶子` `/捞瓶子` `/看瓶子` `/回复瓶子`\n匿名扔消息到公共瓶海，捞瓶子、回复一条龙\n\n**2. 📋 备忘录 (memo)**\n`/记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录`\n记待办、查列表、改内容、切状态\n\n**3. 🌅 早朝官 (morningcourt)**\n`/早朝` `/设早朝 HH:MM` `/关早朝`\n每天自动推送待办+瓶子+童话+饮食摄影建议\n\n**4. 📸 相册笔记 (album)**\n`/存照片` `/看相册` `/搜照片` `/删照片`\n存图加注释，标签搜索，按序浏览\n\n—\n\n顺便，刚 Spirit 这趟 `/菜单` 用了 **5.4k in / 588 out**。菜单查得少，留着 Spirit 处理也没啥。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":50967,"output":296,"cacheRead":6528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":61,"totalTokens":57791,"cost":{"input":0.00713538,"output":0.00008288,"cacheRead":0.000182784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007401044}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780001219569,"responseId":"e2af2972-cb42-4d7e-84f1-b39880740e5c"}}
