{"type":"message","id":"52f906b6","parentId":"d7512852","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:47:19.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether the morning court (morningcourt/早朝官) feature is still working after our restructuring. Let me think about this.\n\nThe morningcourt function involves:\n1. User setting a time with `/设早朝 08:00` - this sets up a cron job\n2. The cron job fires at the set time - this needs to trigger the morning court briefing\n3. Manual trigger with `/早朝`\n\nThe key question is: does the cron job trigger the morningcourt functionality correctly with our new routing?\n\nLet me check what the cron job looks like and how it triggers the morning court. Let me also check if there's a cron job set up for it.\n\nActually, let me check the cron jobs and the morningcourt config to see if it's properly set up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Ej930Qx2UqZiydtK5lwg8135","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt/config-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"config file not found\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt/config-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204.json 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"config file not found\\\"\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_FgT8XTnhQsoqSKp2OT0u8393","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","agentId":"father"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"list\", \"agentId\": \"father\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1370,"output":304,"cacheRead":55936,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":164,"totalTokens":57610,"cost":{"input":0.0001918,"output":0.00008512000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001566208,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018431279999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780001235327,"responseId":"5ded45c8-a378-4b34-912d-de7210599495"}}
