y.md — 确认自己是谁\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\n\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\n\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\n\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。"},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780005600000,"lastRunAtMs":1779993184531,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":126995,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1779996710309},{"id":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678","agentId":"father","sessionKey":"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","name":"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779997894311,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 8 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"session:agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"早朝时间到！用户 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204（汀桑）的早朝播报。请查阅 morningcourt 配置，生成早朝简报并推送给用户。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot1"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780012800000},"updatedAtMs":1779997894311}],"total":2,"offset":0,"limit":2,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null,"deliveryPreviews":{"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9":{"label":"not requested","detail":"not requested"},"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678":{"label":"announce -> qqbot:c2c: