{"type":"message","id":"f56c2523","parentId":"18057a75","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:48:57.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定了。总结一下改了什么：\n\n**1. 当前你的早朝 cron payload 已更新**\n```\n旧: \"早朝时间到！用户xxx的早朝播报。请查阅...\"\n新: [morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation\n```\n\n收到时我一眼就知道谁的事，直接 spawn Son。\n\n**2. Son 的 morningcourt_function.md 新增 cron 格式规范**\n以后新用户 `/设早朝` 时，Son 按这个标准格式组 cron 参数：\n```\ncron job 名: morningcourt-{sender_id}\nsessionTarget: session:agent:father:qqbot:direct:{sender_id}\npayload: [morningcourt] sender_id={sender_id}, trigger briefing generation\n```\n\n**3. Spirit 那边的定义也同步更新了**\n注册和修改时两边一致。\n\n**4. 我的 AGENTS.md 加了「处理 cron 消息」流程**\n明确写了 `[morningcourt]` 前缀怎么识别、怎么 spawn Son。\n\n---\n\n明天 08:00 就能看到实际跑的效果了。如果有问题你到时候喊我调。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":135,"output":257,"cacheRead":62976,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":63368,"cost":{"input":0.000018900000000000002,"output":0.00007196000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001763328,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001854188}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780001333513,"responseId":"348c067a-c864-4dde-900c-a7ef664138fe"}}
