{"type":"message","id":"ad5cab2d","parentId":"f7d68681","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:53:43.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ET_p5oQ7VS9JHtdqjN0ydTJ3893","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config get agents 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor agent in d.get('list', []):\n    if agent.get('id') in ('son', 'spirit'):\n        print(json.dumps(agent, indent=2))\n\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"openclaw config get agents 2>&1 | python3 -c \\\"\\nimport sys, json\\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\\nfor agent in d.get('list', []):\\n    if agent.get('id') in ('son', 'spirit'):\\n        print(json.dumps(agent, indent=2))\\n\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":343,"output":108,"cacheRead":65024,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":65475,"cost":{"input":0.000048020000000000004,"output":0.000030240000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001820672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018989319999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780001621596,"responseId":"49e7e74e-4c1f-4345-8f7e-b20b55553d56"}}
{"type":"message","id":"74470e8c","parentId":"ad5cab2d","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:53:48.417Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_p5oQ7VS9JHtdqjN0ydTJ3893","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"son\",\n  \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-son\",\n  \"model\": {\n    \"primary\": \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\"\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\": {\n      \"alias\": \"QwenVL\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n{\n  \"id\": \"spirit\",\n  \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit\",\n  \"subagents\": {\n    \"allowAgents\": [\n      \"son\"\n    ]\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4705,"aggregated":"{\n  \"id\": \"son\",\n  \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-son\",\n  \"model\": {\n    \"primary\": \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\"\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\": {\n      \"alias\": \"QwenVL\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n{\n  \"id\": \"spirit\",\n  \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit\",\n  \"subagents\": {\n    \"allowAgents\": [\n      \"son\"\n    ]\n  }\n}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780001628416}}
{"type":"message","id":"d57f5ff9","parentId":"74470e8c","timestamp":"2026-05-28T20:53:57.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There it is. Son is explicitly configured to use `dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest` as its primary model. \n\nQwen-vl-max is a vision-language model - it's designed for image understanding tasks. For the album/save-photo feature where Son needs to analyze images, that's appropriate. But for text-only operations like memo list, memo CRUD, floatbottle throw/pickup, and morning court briefing generation, it's completely overkill and wastes tokens.\n\nThe solution: Son should use DeepSeek for text-only operations, and only use Qwen-VL when actually processing images (album features).\n\nThere are a few options:\n1. Set Son's primary model to DeepSeek, and override the model when spawning for image tasks\n2. Leave as-is and accept the waste\n3. Create two separate Son-like agents (one text, one vision)\n\nOption 1 seems most practical. When I spawn Son for text operations, I can let it use its default DeepSeek. When it needs to handle images (存照片), I spawn with the Qwen model override.\n\nWait, but looking at the sessions_list data, Son already uses Qwen for everything including simple memo lists. The sessions show `\"model\": \"qwen-vl-max-latest\"` for all tasks.\n\nLet me suggest to the user that we change Son's primary model to DeepSeek and only use Qwen-VL when images are involved.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了。Son 配置里写死了 `dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"son\",\n  \"model\": {\n    \"primary\": \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n所以连 `/看备忘录` 这种纯文本操作也走视觉模型——明显浪费。\n\n**建议改法：**\n\n把 Son 的默认模型改成 DeepSeek（和你我一样），只有处理图片时才用 Qwen-VL。两种方式：\n\n**方式A：改配置 + spawn 时 override**\n- Son 默认模型 → `deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash`\n- 存照片这种需要看图的任务，我 spawn 时带上 `model` 参数 override 成 Qwen\n\n**方式B：按 action 路由**\n- 不改 Son 配置，改我的 spawn 逻辑——存照片时指定 Qwen，其他一律 DeepSeek\n\n方式A一劳永逸，改完以后我 spawn 传话时加个判断就行。要我改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":207,"output":526,"cacheRead":65408,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":301,"totalTokens":66141,"cost":{"input":0.00002898,"output":0.00014728,"cacheRead":0.001831424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002007684}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780001628429,"responseId":"07978e27-6e75-4518-ae0d-68e80a751b86"}}
