{"type":"message","id":"8572ecef","parentId":"a1d05c4e","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:11:22.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, all three agents are properly configured. Now I need to update my AGENTS.md to note that when spawning Son for image-related tasks (存照片), I should override the model to QwenVL.\n\nLet me update the relevant sections.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"三 Agent 都在，配置正确。现在补一笔 spawn Son 时的模型路由规则到我的 AGENTS.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZZ6vH9vzLTVXM9i8CsrG1314","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"```bash\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"floatbottle\",\"action\":\"throw\",\"params\":{\"content\":\"今天天气真好\"},\"sender_id\":\"汀桑的ID\"}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"spirit\",\n  task: \"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\",\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n```","newText":"```bash\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"floatbottle\",\"action\":\"throw\",\"params\":{\"content\":\"今天天气真好\"},\"sender_id\":\"汀桑的ID\"}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 图片任务：用 QwenVL 模型\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  model: \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"album\",\"action\":\"save\",\"params\":{\"annotation\":\"夕阳\",\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"spirit\",\n  task: \"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\",\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n```\n\n**模型路由规则：**\n\n| Son 任务类型 | 模型 |\n|-------------|------|\n| 纯文本操作（备忘录/漂流瓶/早朝） | DeepSeek（默认） |\n| 图片操作（存照片/看照片/搜照片） | `dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest`（override） |"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"```bash\\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"son\\\",\\n  task: '{\\\"function\\\":\\\"floatbottle\\\",\\\"action\\\":\\\"throw\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\"今天天气真好\\\"},\\\"sender_id\\\":\\\"汀桑的ID\\\"}',\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"spirit\\\",\\n  task: \\\"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\\\",\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n```\",\"newText\":\"```bash\\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"son\\\",\\n  task: '{\\\"function\\\":\\\"floatbottle\\\",\\\"action\\\":\\\"throw\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\"今天天气真好\\\"},\\\"sender_id\\\":\\\"汀桑的ID\\\"}',\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# 图片任务：用 QwenVL 模型\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"son\\\",\\n  model: \\\"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\\\",\\n  task: '{\\\"function\\\":\\\"album\\\",\\\"action\\\":\\\"save\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"annotation\\\":\\\"夕阳\\\",\\\"sender_id\\\":\\\"xxx\\\"}}',\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\\nsessions_spawn(\\n  agentId: \\\"spirit\\\",\\n  task: \\\"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\\\",\\n  mode: \\\"run\\\"\\n)\\n```\\n\\n**模型路由规则：**\\n\\n| Son 任务类型 | 模型 |\\n|-------------|------|\\n| 纯文本操作（备忘录/漂流瓶/早朝） | DeepSeek（默认） |\\n| 图片操作（存照片/看照片/搜照片） | `dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest`（override） |\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":192,"output":650,"cacheRead":73088,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":49,"totalTokens":73930,"cost":{"input":0.00002688,"output":0.000182,"cacheRead":0.002046464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002255344}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780002676031,"responseId":"71780b46-fe72-4a81-bef1-56a191da0cfb"}}
