{"type":"message","id":"5063e4b6","parentId":"7f5e45b8","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:11:24.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定。现在配置是：\n\n| Agent | 模型 | 工作区 |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| **father** (我) | DeepSeek V4 Flash | `workspace-father` |\n| **spirit** (船上电脑) | DeepSeek V4 Flash | `workspace-spirit` |\n| **son** (工作室) | **DeepSeek V4 Flash（默认）** + QwenVL（看图时 override） | `workspace-son` |\n\n以后 spawn Son 的时候：\n- 文字类（捞瓶子、看备忘录）→ 默认 DeepSeek\n- 图片类（存照片、分析图片）→ 我 spawn 时带 `model: \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\"` 参数 override\n\n这样日常操作不走视觉模型，token 省一大截。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":109,"output":181,"cacheRead":73856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":74146,"cost":{"input":0.00001526,"output":0.00005068,"cacheRead":0.002067968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002133908}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780002682263,"responseId":"561c8b2a-cfc7-4555-bec4-0b79be1abf7a"}}
