{"type":"message","id":"dc122b3c","parentId":"aa96fb7f","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:12:11.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to avoid situations like what just happened - where I accidentally overwrote the gateway configuration and lost the other agents. They want to know how to prevent this kind of mistake in the future.\n\nLet me think about what happened:\n1. I tried to update Son's model config using `openclaw config patch --stdin --replace-path agents.list`\n2. The `--replace-path` flag replaced the entire agents.list array with only the son entry\n3. This removed main, father, and spirit from the list\n4. Fortunately, the actual file on disk still had the correct configuration (I'm not sure how - maybe the write was actually to a different layer, or the file wasn't fully overwritten)\n\nSo the user is asking: how do we avoid this kind of thing in the future?\n\nThe answer is several-fold:\n1. Use proper config patch without --replace-path when doing targeted updates\n2. Always validate with --dry-run first\n3. Have a backup/rollback plan\n4. Maybe I should not wield config patching tools carelessly\n\nLet me think about practical safeguards.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"刚才那事说到底是我手滑了。**以后同样的错误可以这么防：**\n\n### 1. 改配置之前先备份\n\n```bash\ncp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak\n```\n\n改了出事直接 `cp .bak` 回来 + `openclaw gateway restart`。\n\n### 2. `--dry-run` 先跑一遍\n\n`openclaw config patch` 有 dry-run 模式，能看到改了啥、会不会删东西。\n\n```\necho '{...}' | openclaw config patch --stdin --dry-run\n```\n\n我刚才要是 dry-run 一下，就能看到 agents.list 只剩 son 了，不会直接 apply。\n\n### 3. `--replace-path` 少用\n\n`--replace-path` 是整个替换数组——用的时候要确保传了**完整列表**。只改一个字段的话直接 `--stdin` 不带 `--replace-path` 就行，递归 merge 不会删别的。\n\n### 4. 涉及到架构变动的操作先让我 spawn 一个子 agent 去干\n\n我自己的 session 里手滑了没回滚，但 spawn 出去干的话，搞砸了关掉那个子 agent 就好，不影响主配置。你下次说\"改 Son 模型\"的时候，我 spawn 一个有 dry-run 的子 agent 去做，确认没问题再 apply。\n\n---\n\n要我给配置文件设个 crontab 定时备份吗？每天自动备份一次 `openclaw.json` 到 `backups/` 目录。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":68940,"output":560,"cacheRead":5248,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":230,"totalTokens":74748,"cost":{"input":0.009651600000000001,"output":0.00015680000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000146944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009955344000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780002723002,"responseId":"04828e6a-c446-41bc-8b93-e186fa3fc5d3"}}
