{"type":"message","id":"7a12c056","parentId":"ae27736e","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:13:17.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about whether the current Dreaming and Morning Court logic still follows their original design. Let me think about what the current state is.\n\nWe've made several changes recently:\n1. Migrated function definitions from Spirit to Son's workspace\n2. Changed Son's default model from QwenVL to DeepSeek\n3. Updated morning court cron payload to be explicit\n4. Updated AGENTS.md to handle morning court cron messages\n5. Updated Dreaming to only process active users from the previous day\n6. Updated registration flow to sync function definitions to Son\n\nBut the fundamental architecture hasn't changed:\n- Dreaming runs at 06:00 via cron, triggered in an isolated session for father\n- Morning court runs at user-set time, triggered via session-targeted cron delivering to father's session with the user\n\nThe key question is: does the user's original design still hold? Let me think about what their original design was.\n\nLooking back at the conversation, the user designed the Trinity architecture:\n- Father (Faye) - reception, routing, chatting\n- Spirit - queries, function definitions, registration\n- Son - execution, data storage\n\nThe recent changes I made:\n1. ✅ Direct routing: Father → Son for daily use (no Spirit intermediary)\n2. ✅ Function definitions moved from Spirit to Son's workspace (functions/)\n3. ✅ Son's default model changed to DeepSeek\n4. ✅ Morning court cron payload is explicit\n5. ✅ Dreaming is incremental (only active users, only one day)\n6. ✅ Registration still goes through Spirit, then syncs to Son\n\nSo the architecture still follows the original design, just optimized to cut Spirit out of the daily execution path. The core Trinity structure is intact.\n\nLet me just confirm by checking the current state of things.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"放心，四位一体架构没动，只是优化了几条路径。对比一下你原来的设计和现在的状态：\n\n| 模块 | 你原来的设计 | 现在 | 变了没 |\n|------|------------|------|--------|\n| **Dreaming** | 每天 06:00，回顾自己→遍历用户→更新心境→写梦 | 一样，只是改成了**增量模式**（只读前一天活跃用户） | 微调 |\n| **早朝官** | cron 定时触发 → Father 处理 → 推送用户 | 一样，cron payload 写成 `[morningcourt] sender_id=xxx`，更明确 | 微调 |\n| **Father 路由** | 新面孔问名字 → 读 trigger_prompt → 路由 | 没变 | 没变 |\n| **Spirit 职责** | 查功能定义、注册、删除 | 没变，**注册/删除依然走 Spirit** | 没变 |\n| **Son 职责** | 按定义执行，干脏活累活 | 没变 | 没变 |\n| **调用流程** | 注册：Spirit → Son / 日常：Spirit → Son | **日常改成了 Father → Son 直达**，注册不变 | 优化 |\n\n**唯一的结构变化**是日常调用绕过了 Spirit——但你前面对这个改动是同意的。注册和删除还是 Spirit 的活，架构没崩。\n\n早朝的 cron job 我确认一下当前状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_nF6iY0UBpFzXwb7Hk5kQ5734","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"get\", \"jobId\": \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6439,"output":763,"cacheRead":68096,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":369,"totalTokens":75298,"cost":{"input":0.0009014600000000001,"output":0.00021364000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001906688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003021788}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780002787208,"responseId":"e8282de9-ca27-4ce7-a9f8-f468a7ed707c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bfa9a8c","parentId":"7a12c056","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:13:18.123Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_nF6iY0UBpFzXwb7Hk5kQ5734","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204\",\n  \"name\": \"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1779997894311,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"session:agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n    \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n    \"accountId\": \"bot1\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780012800000\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780001312129\n}"}],"details":{"id":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678","agentId":"father","sessionKey":"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","name":"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779997894311,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 8 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"session:agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot1"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780012800000},"updatedAtMs":1780001312129},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780002798117