{"type":"message","id":"37ab7e22","parentId":"1bfa9a8c","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:13:22.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The morning court cron is configured correctly for tomorrow 08:00. \n\nLet me summarize for the user - their design is intact, the two changes I made were explicitly agreed upon:\n\n1. Incremental dreaming (only active users, one day) - the user said \"应该还好吧 dream不涉及到多agent调用\" which was agreement\n2. Direct Father → Son for daily use - the user explicitly said \"对 那就把spirit的xxx_function.md先迁移过去到son\"\n\nEverything else is exactly as the user designed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"早朝 cron 明天 08:00 准时触发，格式正确。\n\n回过头看你原本的设计，我动的其实就两处：\n\n1. **Dreaming 改成增量** — 你说\"应该还好\"但我说改成增量了，你当时也没反对\n2. **日常调用绕 Spirit** — 你亲口说\"对，那就迁移过去\"\n\n其他所有东西——你设计的四位一体结构、Father 认人、Spirit 管注册删除、Son 干活、早朝 cron 推送到 QQ——全都没动。\n\n要说\"还是不是你设计的那套\"——是，只是把 Spirit 从日常路径里踢出去了，这也是你拍的板。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":418,"output":251,"cacheRead":75264,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":109,"totalTokens":75933,"cost":{"input":0.00005852,"output":0.00007028000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002107392,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002236192}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780002798151,"responseId":"cfb52cf6-ba37-42a8-9527-9e6351e9897c"}}
