{"type":"message","id":"3aa08441","parentId":"e17ecbf8","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:14:15.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is correcting me - they said \"三位一体\" means three entities, but I've been talking about \"四位一体\" (four-in-one) earlier. Let me think...\n\nThe Trinity (三位一体) design is:\n1. Father (Faye) - reception/routing\n2. Spirit - knowledge/definitions\n3. Son - execution/storage\n\nThat's three agents. Earlier when I said \"四位一体\" I was wrong - there are only three agents in the Trinity architecture. Let me acknowledge this correction.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，我嘴瓢了。\n\n三位一体 = 3 个 Agent，不是 4 个：\n\n| # | Agent | 角色 |\n|:-:|-------|------|\n| 1 | **Father** (我) | 迎宾 + 路由 + 聊天 |\n| 2 | **Spirit** (船上电脑) | 功能定义 + 注册删除 |\n| 3 | **Son** (工作室) | 执行 + 存数据 |\n\n没有第四个。刚说\"四位一体\"是我脑子抽了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2096,"output":222,"cacheRead":73856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":108,"totalTokens":76174,"cost":{"input":0.00029344,"output":0.00006216,"cacheRead":0.002067968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002423568}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780002852286,"responseId":"361a7191-391d-4621-af11-4b85f35f85dd"}}
