{"type":"message","id":"8990872d","parentId":"cfa4e07b","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:15:37.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the bindings documentation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZkGvTbibtTrLKj8JCCaQ0189","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/gateway/configuration.md","offset":1,"limit":50},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/gateway/configuration.md\", \"offset\": 1, \"limit\": 50}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":473,"output":99,"cacheRead":78080,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":9,"totalTokens":78652,"cost":{"input":0.00006622,"output":0.000027720000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00218624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0022801799999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780002935847,"responseId":"3db565d4-375d-4c08-9b98-9e087b937d90"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dde1ed38","parentId":"8990872d","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:15:37.781Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ZkGvTbibtTrLKj8JCCaQ0189","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"Configuration overview: common tasks, quick setup, and links to the full reference\"\nread_when:\n  - Setting up OpenClaw for the first time\n  - Looking for common configuration patterns\n  - Navigating to specific config sections\ntitle: \"Configuration\"\n---\n\nOpenClaw reads an optional <Tooltip tip=\"JSON5 supports comments and trailing commas\">**JSON5**</Tooltip> config from `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`.\nThe active config path must be a regular file. Symlinked `openclaw.json`\nlayouts are unsupported for OpenClaw-owned writes; an atomic write may replace\nthe path instead of preserving the symlink. If you keep config outside the\ndefault state directory, point `OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH` directly at the real file.\n\nIf the file is missing, OpenClaw uses safe defaults. Common reasons to add a config:\n\n- Connect channels and control who can message the bot\n- Set models, tools, sandboxing, or automation (cron, hooks)\n- Tune sessions, media, networking, or UI\n\nSee the [full reference](/gateway/configuration-reference) for every available field.\n\nAgents and automation should use `config.schema.lookup` for exact field-level\ndocs before editing config. Use this page for task-oriented guidance and\n[Configuration reference](/gateway/configuration-reference) for the broader\nfield map and defaults.\n\n<Tip>\n**New to configuration?** Start with `openclaw onboard` for interactive setup, or check out the [Configuration Examples](/gateway/configuration-examples) guide for complete copy-paste configs.\n</Tip>\n\n## Minimal config\n\n```json5\n// ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n{\n  agents: { defaults: { workspace: \"~/.openclaw/workspace\" } },\n  channels: { whatsapp: { allowFrom: [\"+15555550123\"] } },\n}\n```\n\n## Editing config\n\n<Tabs>\n  <Tab title=\"Interactive wizard\">\n    ```bash\n    openclaw onboard       # full onboarding flow\n    openclaw configure     # config wizard\n    ```\n\n[689 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780002937781}}
{"type":"message","id":"97569623","parentId":"dde1ed38","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:15:39.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for the bindings section in the configuration docs.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_OspVa3QR0wwZ5jcmz2oh6061","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"bindings\\|route.*agentId\\|route.*channel\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/gateway/configuration.md 2>/dev/null | head -20"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -n \\\"bindings\\\\|route.*agentId\\\\|route.*channel\\\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/gateway/configuration.md 2>/dev/null | head -20\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":535,"output":97,"cacheRead":78592,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":13,"totalTokens":79224,"cost":{"input":0.0000749,"output":0.00002716,"cacheRead":0.002200576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023026360000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780002937792,"responseId":"11575e60-5dbc-4e4c-916b-a7fc1811acf4"}}
