{"type":"message","id":"0c03a206","parentId":"6b4052bc","timestamp":"2026-05-28T21:16:44.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The config is valid and everything looks good. Let me summarize:\n\n1. Config validation passed ✅\n2. Gateway running, 3 agents configured ✅\n3. QQ Bot ON with 3 accounts ✅\n4. Bindings routing all qqbot to father ✅\n5. Son's primary model now DeepSeek (the last subagent using Qwen was 3h ago) ✅\n\nThe current session is active and talking to me right now, so everything is working properly.\n\nOne thing to note: there's a new version available (2026.5.27). I should mention that.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置没毛病，逐项确认：\n\n**Config 验证：** ✅ 通过\n\n**Gateway 状态：** ✅ 正常（3 Agent，62 个 sessions）\n\n**QQ Bot 通道：** ✅ 在线，3 个账号正常\n\n**Bindings 路由：**\n- bot1 → father ✅\n- bot2 → father ✅\n- bot3 → father ✅\n\n**各 Agent 模型：**\n- Father → DeepSeek V4 Flash ✅\n- Spirit → DeepSeek V4 Flash ✅\n- Son → **DeepSeek V4 Flash（默认）** + QwenVL（备选）✅ — 刚才改对了\n\n**Son 实际调用确认：** 最近的子 session 已经是 DeepSeek 跑了，上一个用 Qwen 的是 3 小时前（改之前的事）。\n\n**另外提醒：** OpenClaw 有新版 `2026.5.27` 可以升，要跑 `openclaw update` 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1769,"output":333,"cacheRead":83968,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":123,"totalTokens":86070,"cost":{"input":0.00024766,"output":0.00009324000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002351104,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002692004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780002999893,"responseId":"63722fbc-ee79-4864-baf8-64a0162500cf"}}
