{"type":"message","id":"87eb88ad","parentId":"a6679ae7","timestamp":"2026-05-29T00:01:03.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The morning court briefing has been generated by Son. It was completed successfully. The cron has delivery mode \"announce\" to the user's QQ, so the result will be delivered directly to 汀桑's QQ chat.\n\nLooking at the result:\n- 16.2k tokens (13.9k in / 2.2k out) - using DeepSeek now instead of QwenVL, but still significant because the morning court involves generating a fairy tale and reading multiple data sources.\n- Content looks good - has today's todo, a bottle from the sea, a mini fairy tale, food recommendation, photography recommendation.\n\nThe cron's delivery mode is \"announce\" with the target set to qqbot c2c, and Son's output was routed back. But the announce delivery on the cron job should handle the final delivery.\n\nActually, looking at the inter-session message, it says the result is routed by OpenClaw. Since the cron job has delivery.announce set to qqbot, the result should be automatically sent to the user. But since this came to me (the parent session) as an inter-session message, I should check whether it's been delivered or if I need to do something.\n\nSince I'm the parent session and this is a notification from the subagent, and the cron job has announce delivery configured, the delivery should happen automatically. But the instruction says \"Review/verify the result\" and \"If the agent should message the user itself, check that the job has a usable route.\"\n\nLooking at the cron job:\n```json\n\"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n    \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n    \"accountId\": \"bot1\"\n}\n```\n\nThe delivery mode is \"announce\" which means OpenClaw will deliver the final reply to the user. So I just need to provide my reply and OpenClaw will handle the announcement.\n\nThe result looks good. Let me just respond with the morning court briefing so it gets delivered to the user via the announce mechanism.\n\nActually wait - the cron job's delivery is \"announce\" with to/from set. This means when the cron fires, my final reply in this turn gets sent to the user. So I should just output the morning court briefing as my reply.\n\nBut actually, this is a yielded turn where the subagent completed. The subagent result is inter-session data. I should provide a user-facing update. Since the announce delivery will take my final reply and send it to the user's QQ, I should simply output the morning court briefing.\n\nLet me just pass through Son's result.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🌅 **早朝官报到！**\n\n📋 今日待办：\n1. [待办] 记得投递深圳科创学院简历6月20号以前\n\n🌊 瓶海一瞥：\n🍾 捞到一个瓶子 — \"今天南坪快速通道爆炸了...\"\n\n📖 今日童话：\n夏天的早晨，太阳刚升起，小蒲公英种子就要出发了。妈妈对它说：\"勇敢一点，风会带你去最好的地方。\"小种子飞过城市的高楼，越过大河，最后轻轻落在一片温暖的山坡上。它想：这里就是我要努力的地方。它深深扎根，努力生长。一个月后，它开出了一朵灿烂的小黄花。\n\n🥗 今日饮食建议：\n五月末深圳闷热多雨，宜食清凉解暑之物，如苦瓜、冬瓜、绿豆汤。多补水，少辛辣，护脾胃。\n\n📸 今日摄影建议：\n清晨柔和光线适合拍摄花草上的露珠；傍晚不妨到公园捕捉夕阳穿过树叶的光影。\n\n祝君一日顺利 ☀️"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":698,"output":789,"cacheRead":89600,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":571,"totalTokens":91087,"cost":{"input":0.00009772,"output":0.00022092000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0025088,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0028274399999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780012854173,"responseId":"e7c74dc1-ed50-4262-89da-a61f717d4eab"}}
