{"type":"message","id":"9a9caea0","parentId":"6fb737a2","timestamp":"2026-05-29T05:25:52.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The morning court cron fired again at 1:25 PM instead of 08:00. That's strange. Let me check what's happening with the cron job - maybe there's an issue with the schedule.\n\nWait, it's 13:25 now, not 08:00. The cron was set to `0 8 * * *` (08:00 daily). Let me check if the cron job is still correct or if something went wrong.\n\nActually, looking at the previous message at 08:00, the user asked \"在线吗，回来了吗\" at some point after that. The current time is 13:25. So the cron fired again at 13:25?\n\nLet me check the cron job to see what's going on.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"等等，13:25 又触发了？我看一眼 cron 状态。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xDuEMZiYRgUMs8wBy6Jj6025","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"get\", \"jobId\": \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":476,"output":252,"cacheRead":89600,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":156,"totalTokens":90328,"cost":{"input":0.00006664,"output":0.00007056,"cacheRead":0.0025088,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002646}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780032349843,"responseId":"66b45de3-8a14-499e-80db-722f65b6e9e9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cad320aa","parentId":"9a9caea0","timestamp":"2026-05-29T05:25:53.136Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_xDuEMZiYRgUMs8wBy6Jj6025","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204\",\n  \"name\": \"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1779997894311,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"session:agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n    \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n    \"accountId\": \"bot1\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780099200000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780012800016,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 26714,\n    \"lastDelivered\": false,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n    \"runningAtMs\": 1780032340630\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780012826730\n}"}],"details":{"id":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678","agentId":"father","sessionKey":"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","name":"morningcourt-6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779997894311,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 8 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"session:agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot1"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780099200000,"lastRunAtMs":1780012800016,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":26714,"lastDelivered":false,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-delivered","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"runningAtMs":1780032340630},"updatedAtMs":1780012826730},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780032353128}}
{"type":"message","id":"b29df331","parentId":"cad320aa","timestamp":"2026-05-29T05:25:58.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the cron state:\n- `nextRunAtMs: 1780099200000` - this is the next scheduled run\n- `lastRunAtMs: 1780012800016` - last run was at 08:00\n- `runningAtMs: 1780032340630` - this is the current time, 13:25\n\nThe cron schedule is `0 8 * * *` (08:00) and `lastRunAtMs` shows it ran at 08:00. But the current time is 13:25 and it's firing again. The `runningAtMs` suggests it's currently running.\n\nWait - this isn't a second fire of the cron. Looking more carefully at `lastDelivered: false` and `lastDeliveryStatus: \"not-delivered\"` - the 08:00 run didn't deliver! It's retrying because the delivery failed.\n\nActually, I think what happened is the cron fired at 08:00, I processed it via spawning Son, but the delivery status shows \"not-delivered\". This might mean the delivery didn't complete properly, and the system is re-triggering it.\n\nActually, looking at `lastDelivered: false` and `lastDeliveryStatus: \"not-delivered\"` - this indicates the previous delivery at 08:00 didn't successfully deliver to the user's QQ. The system may have queued a retry.\n\nBut wait, I just processed the 08:00 run and Son generated the morning court briefing, which was delivered to the user's QQ (the user responded \"在线吗，回来了吗\" which means they saw it). So the data delivery was successful.\n\nHmm, the `runningAtMs: 1780032340630` suggests this is a new trigger that's currently running. Let me check if there's a separate cron event system that re-triggers failed deliveries.\n\nActually, I think this might be a duplicate/scheduled re-fire. The cron system sees the last delivery as \"not-delivered\" (maybe it wasn't marked as delivered properly), and is trying again.\n\nEither way, the user already got their morning court at 08:00. Let me not generate another one - I'll just spawn Son again to be safe but actually, it would be weird to send another briefing in the afternoon.\n\nLet me just tell the user what's happening and skip the duplicate.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"是早上的 cron 重试了。看日志：\n\n- `lastRunAtMs: 08:00` → 今早正常触发 ✅\n- `lastDeliveryStatus: \"not-delivered\"` → 但系统标记为\"未送达\"\n- 所以现在 13:25 又重试了一次\n\n你早上已经收到简报了对吧？这是重复触发。我把它按住。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":581,"output":586,"cacheRead":90240,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":501,"totalTokens":91407,"cost":{"input":0.00008134,"output":0.00016408000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00252672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00277214}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780032353158,"responseId":"537cde87-d1af-4cd4-8dd5-60801f72a0ac"}}
