{"type":"message","id":"dc94d29a","parentId":"c2c006da","timestamp":"2026-05-29T05:27:12.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Son subagent has completed generating the morning court briefing. Now I need to deliver this to the user. Since the cron at 08:00 failed to deliver, let me make sure the user gets it this time by sending it directly in this session.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🌅 **早朝官报到！**\n\n📋 今日待办：\n1. [待办] 记得投递深圳科创学院简历（截止6月20日）\n\n🌊 瓶海一瞥：\n🍾 捞到一个瓶子 — \"🐘 小大象的云朵帽子...\"\n\n📖 今日童话：\n小蜗牛慢慢想爬最高的梧桐树，伙伴们都笑它太慢。慢慢不急，每天背着小房子往上爬一寸。雨天缩进壳里听雨声，大风贴紧树皮等风过。一个月后的清晨，慢慢终于爬到树顶。朝阳升起，满城风光尽收眼底。原来最远的不是路，是不敢出发的心。\n\n🥗 今日饮食建议：\n5月末夏初宜清淡养心，多吃苦瓜、黄瓜、番茄等清热利湿的蔬果，少食油腻辛辣，一碗绿豆汤最解暑气。\n\n📸 今日摄影建议：\n初夏阳光充足，午后柔和光线适合拍荷花初绽；清晨朝露未干时，逆光拍绿叶上的水珠最出片。\n\n祝君一日顺利 ☀️  \n\n早上那趟 delivery 标记未送达，我查一下是什么原因让推送没成功。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_T3LwdSrnVjPzLk8w45oa4513","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"get\", \"jobId\": \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1666,"output":387,"cacheRead":91392,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":52,"totalTokens":93445,"cost":{"input":0.00023324,"output":0.00010836000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002558976,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002900576}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780032428768,"responseId":"aa467cb5-60ab-49c1-8e36-3a010eebd48a"}}
