bottle content starts with \\\"🐘 小大象的云朵帽子\\\" - that's about 9-10 characters. The full content has more text. Let me just use \\\"🐘 小大象的云朵帽子\\\" as the summary (it's the title).\\n\\nNow let me assemble the full response.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Now I have all the data. Let me assemble the briefing.\\n\\n🌅 早朝官报到！\\n\\n📋 今日待办：\\n1. [待办] 记得投递深圳科创学院简历（截止6月20日）\\n\\n🌊 瓶海一瞥：\\n🍾 捞到一个瓶子 — \\\"🐘 小大象的云朵帽子...\\\"\\n\\n📖 今日童话：\\n小蜗牛慢慢想爬最高的梧桐树，伙伴们都笑它太慢。慢慢不急，每天背着小房子往上爬一寸。雨天缩进壳里听雨声，大风贴紧树皮等风过。一个月后的清晨，慢慢终于爬到树顶。朝阳升起，满城风光尽收眼底。原来最远的不是路，是不敢出发的心。\\n\\n🥗 今日饮食建议：\\n5月末夏初宜清淡养心，多吃苦瓜、黄瓜、番茄等清热利湿的蔬果，少食油腻辛辣，一碗绿豆汤最解暑气。\\n\\n📸 今日摄影建议：\\n初夏阳光充足，午后柔和光线适合拍荷花初绽；清晨朝露未干时，逆光拍绿叶上的水珠最出片。\\n\\n祝君一日顺利 ☀️\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n          \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n          \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 135,\n            \"output\": 410,\n            \"totalTokens\": 14369,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13824,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.000520772\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1780032421914,\n          \"responseId\": \"a7133df7-8e79-4d23-af82-36a0db3b9e58\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"db19f04a\",\n            \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780032425455,\n            \"seq\": 17\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"visibility\": {\n    \"mode\": \"tree\",\n    \"restricted\": true,\n    \"warning\": \"Session visibility is restricted (effective tools.sessions.visibility=tree). Results may omit sessions outside the current scope. The count field reflects only sessions within the current scope.\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"count":2,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204","agentId":"father","kind":"other","channel":"qqbot","origin":{"provider":"qqbot","a