ually chatted with me yet, so I can't really \"pass a message\" easily\n\nActually, wait - I should just relay the message. Since the QQ bot routes through me (Father), I can send a message to 雾籽米's QQ. But I need to know which bot account 雾籽米 is talking to.\n\nLet me check if there's any session or delivery info for 雾籽米.\n\nActually, I think I'm overcomplicating this. Let me just tell 汀桑 that 雾籽米 hasn't actually messaged me yet, so I don't have a way to pass the message to them right now. Unless 汀桑 can tell me more about how to reach them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哦——让我传话给雾籽米问ta学校哪有巧乐兹卖。\n\n问题是我跟雾籽米还没正儿八经聊过天，ta没给我发过消息，我这边没有ta的活跃会话，没法主动推送过去。\n\n你知道雾籽米的QQ号或者ta用的是哪个bot账号联系我的吗？或者ta平时是通过什么方式找你的？我看看能不能从那边递过去。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1296,"output":730,"cacheRead":101632,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":643,"totalTokens":103658,"cost":{"input":0.00018144000000000002,"output":0.0002044,"cacheRead":0.002845696,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003231536}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780036930418,"responseId":"ae9a895e-00a3-4064-9510-3c671bc98fe9"}}
