{"type":"message","id":"f838dd0f","parentId":"db61563e","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:44:15.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying I'm slow at responding and they want a feature to pass messages to other users. Let me think about this.\n\nThe current problem is:\n1. 雾籽米 uses bot2, and has never sent me a message\n2. I can't proactively push messages to users who haven't interacted with me\n3. The user wants me to relay a message to 雾籽米 asking where to buy 巧乐兹 at school\n\nThe user also mentioned they might want this as a feature - a way to pass messages to other users of the system.\n\nLet me think about how to design this:\n\n1. **Store pending messages** - I could store messages in a file per recipient\n2. **When the recipient next sends a message** - I check for pending messages and deliver them\n3. **This would work as a \"message relay\" feature**\n\nActually, for this specific case with 雾籽米, the simplest approach might be:\n- I know 雾籽米 uses bot2\n- If I could somehow queue a message for them\n- When they next message bot2 → Father (me) → I check pending → I deliver the message\n\nLet me propose a simple design:\n\n**功能：消息转达（message relay）**\n\n```\n记录格式：~/.openclaw/workspace-father/message_relay/{recipient_id}.jsonl\n每条记录：{ from: sender_id, message: \"内容\", timestamp: \"...\", delivered: false }\n\n流程：\n1. 用户A说\"帮我给XXX带话：内容\"\n2. 我确认XXX是谁（查users/或让用户指定）\n3. 写入 message_relay/{recipient_id}.jsonl\n4. 回复用户A：\"话我记住了，等XXX上线我转告ta\"\n5. XXX下次给我发消息时 → 我先读 pending messages → 逐条转达 → 标记 delivered\n```\n\nFor right now though, the immediate issue is that the user thinks I'm slow. Let me just handle this directly. I can't proactively message 雾籽米 through bot2 because they've never messaged me, but I can set up a pending message system.\n\nLet me propose this as a new feature to register.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，反应确实慢——主要是我没法主动找雾籽米说话，ta没来过我就只能干等着。\n\n这事可以做成一个功能。你之前不是说想注册新功能吗，刚好：\n\n---\n\n**功能提案：消息转达（/递话）**\n\n```\n/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>\n→ 我把话存下来，等对方下次找我时转告ta\n→ 对方收到时会显示\"汀桑托我带话：……\"\n\n/看递话\n→ 查看我还没转出去的话\n```\n\n**数据结构**（存在 Son 那边）：\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace-son/messenger/\n└── pending.jsonl\n```\n\n每条：`{from: \"汀桑\", from_sender: \"6687...\", to: \"雾籽米\", to_sender: \"346E...\", message: \"你学校哪有巧乐兹卖\", timestamp: \"...\", delivered: false}`\n\n---\n\n要注册这个功能吗？注册完之后：\n\n1. 我先把你这句\"哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方\"存进去\n2. 等雾籽米下次找bot2说话，我一查有pending消息，直接转过去\n\n省得你干等。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":624,"output":724,"cacheRead":102528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":465,"totalTokens":103876,"cost":{"input":0.00008736,"output":0.00020272,"cacheRead":0.002870784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031608639999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780037046104,"responseId":"35fbe4e9-7012-497d-8988-c6c2ac2db87e"}}
