{"type":"message","id":"34a01862","parentId":"aef9aa07","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:49:12.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can deliver the message to 雾籽米 now. But according to my message delivery logic, I need to wait for 雾籽米 (sender_id: 346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D) to send me a message first through bot2. I can't proactively send them a message.\n\nLet me check if the new user (468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B) is 雾籽米 or a different person. From what I found earlier:\n- 雾籽米: sender_id = 346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D - existing user, registered earlier\n- New user: sender_id = 468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B - came at 13:46 today\n\nThese are two different people. The current conversation is with 汀桑 (6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204).\n\nSo I still need to wait for 雾籽米 to contact me first before I can deliver the message.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"还没法主动送——我得等雾籽米（bot2那条线）先来找我，我才能把话转过去。我不能主动给ta发消息。\n\n不过目前我们有三个用户了：\n\n| 称呼 | sender_id | 状态 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| **汀桑**（你） | 6687D4... ✅ | 聊得火热 |\n| **雾籽米** | 346E6B... ⏳ | 注册了但还没正式聊过 |\n| **新朋友**（13:46来的） | 468B72... ❓ | 问了菜单就断了，名字还没问 |\n\n雾籽米那边的话我已经存好了，ta一来bot2打招呼我就递过去。新朋友那边……ta要是再回来我就问个名字。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":105568,"output":419,"cacheRead":3584,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":251,"totalTokens":109571,"cost":{"input":0.01477952,"output":0.00011732000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000100352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014997192000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780037341386,"responseId":"74d25ff9-15ce-4529-8fcf-ea029cc63c42"}}
