{"type":"message","id":"f36538fe","parentId":"3947cff2","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:51:35.033Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to update my AGENTS.md to use the cron-based active delivery approach for message passing, instead of just waiting for the recipient to message me.\n\nThe logic would be:\n1. User says `/递话 <称呼> <内容>` \n2. I find the recipient's user info (sender_id, which bot account they use)\n3. I create a one-shot cron job with `deleteAfterRun: true` that fires in 1 minute\n4. The cron uses `delivery: {mode: \"announce\", channel: \"qqbot\", to: \"qqbot:c2c:{recipient_sender_id}\", accountId: \"{their_bot}\"}`\n5. The payload contains the message from the sender\n6. Reply to the original user: \"话已递出\"\n\nThe tricky part is knowing which bot account the recipient uses. Looking at the bindings:\n- bot1 → father\n- bot2 → father\n- bot3 → father\n\nAll three qqbot accounts route to me. But for delivery to a specific user, I need to know which account they're associated with. Actually, from the pending.jsonl, I already have the `to_id` (sender_id). But I don't have the account_id (which bot) for the recipient.\n\nHmm, actually I could infer this from the User.md or from the channel routing. Or I could try all three bot accounts... that would be wasteful.\n\nActually, looking at the cron I just created, I used `accountId: \"bot2\"` for 雾籽米 - but how did I know it's bot2? The user told me earlier \"他用bot2\". But for unknown users, I wouldn't know.\n\nLet me think about this differently. The sessions_send tool says \"Creates missing configured-agent main session\" when sending to an agentId. But what about sending to a user's session?\n\nActually, looking at the sessions_send description more carefully:\n- It sends to a session by sessionKey/label\n- Or to a configured agent by agentId\n- Creates missing configured-agent main session\n\nFor delivering to a user who hasn't messaged me yet, I don't have a sessionKey. But all qqbot messages route to me (father). \n\nActually, looking at the delivery mechanism in cron, it uses `channel: \"qqbot\"`, `to: \"qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}\"`, `accountId: \"bot1/2/3\"`. So the key is knowing which bot account the recipient uses.\n\nBut wait - for users who haven't messaged me, I wouldn't know which bot account they're on. The User.md doesn't store that info. We could add it.\n\nAlternatively, I could try a delivery without specifying accountId and let the system figure it out from the channel routing. Or... hmm.\n\nLet me just update the AGENTS.md with the cron-based approach, and note that for the accountId we can figure it out or store it. For now, the approach works with the data we have.\n\nActually, let me re-read the AGENTS.md 3.5 section that I just wrote and replace it with the cron-based approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_mVffpxW3L5mBYXvjlxVB3034","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":198,"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"limit\": 20, \"offset\": 198, \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2973,"output":754,"cacheRead":108800,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":666,"totalTokens":112527,"cost":{"input":0.00041622,"output":0.00021112000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0030464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00367374}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780037486735,"responseId":"7849cad9-835d-401e-a8be-1c399bc3eaa9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f94ae0b0","parentId":"f36538fe","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:51:35.345Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_mVffpxW3L5mBYXvjlxVB3034","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  → Son 组装完整早朝简报\n  → 直接 deliver 给用户（cron 已设好 announce delivery）\n```\n\n### 3.5 消息转达（/递话）\n\n跨用户异步带话功能，不涉及 Son/Spirit，我自己处理。\n\n#### 存话流程\n\n```\n触发: 用户说 \"/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>\" 或明确表达让带话的意图\n\n→ 从 User.md 知道当前说话的人（from）\n→ 模糊匹配 users/ 下所有目录，找称呼匹配的 user（to_id + to_name）\n  - 找到 → 继续\n  - 没找到 → 回复用户：\"我不认识叫这个的人\"\n→ append 到 messenger/pending.jsonl：\n   {\"from_id\":\"xxx\",\"from_name\":\"汀桑\",\"to_id\":\"yyy\",\"to_name\":\"雾籽米\",\"message\":\"...\",\"timestamp\":\"...\",\"delivered\":false}\n→ 回复用户：\"话我记住了，等ta找我时帮你转达\"\n\n[244 more lines in file. Use offset=218 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780037495344}}
{"type":"message","id":"72e32f7c","parentId":"f94ae0b0","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:51:46.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I need to rewrite section 3.5 to use the cron-based active push approach instead of just waiting. The new logic:\n\n1. User says `/递话 <称呼> <内容>` or expresses intent\n2. I look up the recipient from users/ directory by their name\n3. I need to know which bot account they use - I should store this in User.md or figure it out\n4. Create a one-shot cron with deleteAfterRun: true, scheduled to fire in ~1 minute\n5. The cron delivers the message via announce to the recipient's QQ\n6. Reply to the user: \"话已递出\"\n\nThe question is - how to know which bot account to use for the recipient? Let me think...\n\nOptions:\n1. Store `bot_channel` in User.md (like `bot1`, `bot2`, `bot3` - set when they first message me)\n2. Try broadcasting to all bots\n3. Add a parameter to `/递话` like `/递话 雾籽米 bot2 你学校有巧乐兹吗`\n\nOption 1 makes the most sense - when I recognize a new user, I record which bot they came through. The bindings tell me that all qqbot routes go to father, but within qqbot there are multiple accounts. When a user messages me via bot2, I can record that.\n\nActually, looking at the inbound metadata format from earlier, it has `account_id: \"bot1\"` in the top-level metadata. So when a message comes in, I can see which bot account it came through and save that to User.md.\n\nLet me write this up properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HfE351IS3FbDHM1BronG4424","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### 3.5 消息转达（/递话）\n\n跨用户异步带话功能，不涉及 Son/Spirit，我自己处理。\n\n#### 存话流程\n\n```\n触发: 用户说 \"/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>\" 或明确表达让带话的意图\n\n→ 从 User.md 知道当前说话的人（from）\n→ 模糊匹配 users/ 下所有目录，找称呼匹配的 user（to_id + to_name）\n  - 找到 → 继续\n  - 没找到 → 回复用户：\"我不认识叫这个的人\"\n→ append 到 messenger/pending.jsonl：\n   {\"from_id\":\"xxx\",\"from_name\":\"汀桑\",\"to_id\":\"yyy\",\"to_name\":\"雾籽米\",\"message\":\"...\",\"timestamp\":\"...\",\"delivered\":false}\n→ 回复用户：\"话我记住了，等ta找我时帮你转达\"\n```\n\n#### 递话流程\n\n已合并在 Step 0 中：每次收到任何用户的消息，先查 messenger/pending.jsonl 中有无给 ta 的未递消息。\n\n有的话先转告再处理ta的本意：\n\n> \"有人托我带话——\n> 汀桑说：你学校哪有卖巧乐兹的地方\"","newText":"### 3.5 消息转达（/递话）\n\n跨用户异步带话功能，不涉及 Son/Spirit，我自己处理。\n\n#### 用户入话通道记录\n\n每次用户首次发消息时，在 User.md 中记录 ta 走的 bot 通道：\n\n```\n# 从 inbound metadata 读取\naccount_id = bot1/bot2/bot3  # 看消息是从哪个QQ机器人来的\n```\n\n存入 User.md：\n```\n- **QQ号:** {sender_id}\n- **bot通道:** bot1  ← 新增这行\n```\n\n这样后续递话时就知道用哪个 bot 推送。\n\n#### 存话 + 递话流程\n\n```\n触发: 用户说 \"/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>\" 或明确表达让带话的意图\n\nStep 1: 认人\n  → 从 User.md 知道当前说话的人是谁（from_id + from_name）\n  → 模糊匹配 users/ 下所有目录，找称呼匹配的 user（to_id + to_name）\n    - 找到 → 继续\n    - 没找到 → 回复用户：\"我不认识叫这个的人\"\n\nStep 2: 查对方的 bot 通道\n  → 读 users/{to_id}/User.md，找 \"bot通道:\" 字段\n  → 拿到 account_id（bot1/bot2/bot3）\n\nStep 3: 创建一次性 cron 主动推送\n  → cron 参数：\n      名称: deliver-{from_name}-{to_name}\n      时间: 1分钟后（如 \"now + 1min\"）\n      payload: \"{from_name}托我带话：{内容}\"\n      sessionTarget: isolated\n      delivery: {\n        mode: announce,\n        channel: qqbot,\n        to: qqbot:c2c:{to_id},\n        accountId: {对方的bot通道}\n      }\n      deleteAfterRun: true\n\nStep 4: 回复发话人\n  → \"话已递出 ✅\"\n```\n\n#### cron 触发后的处理\n\n一次性 cron 触发时，创建 isolated session 推送消息。系统自动将 payload 内容通过 announce 送到目标用户的 QQ。\n不需要我额外处理。\n\n**不再用 `pending.jsonl` 被动等待。** 改用一次性 cron 主动推送。"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"### 3.5 消息转达（/递话）\\n\\n跨用户异步带话功能，不涉及 Son/Spirit，我自己处理。\\n\\n#### 存话流程\\n\\n```\\n触发: 用户说 \\\"/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>\\\" 或明确表达让带话的意图\\n\\n→ 从 User.md 知道当前说话的人（from）\\n→ 模糊匹配 users/ 下所有目录，找称呼匹配的 user（to_id + to_name）\\n  - 找到 → 继续\\n  - 没找到 → 回复用户：\\\"我不认识叫这个的人\\\"\\n→ append 到 messenger/pending.jsonl：\\n   {\\\"from_id\\\":\\\"xxx\\\",\\\"from_name\\\":\\\"汀桑\\\",\\\"to_id\\\":\\\"yyy\\\",\\\"to_name\\\":\\\"雾籽米\\\",\\\"message\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"delivered\\\":false}\\n→ 回复用户：\\\"话我记住了，等ta找我时帮你转达\\\"\\n```\\n\\n#### 递话流程\\n\\n已合并在 Step 0 中：每次收到任何用户的消息，先查 messenger/pending.jsonl 中有无给 ta 的未递消息。\\n\\n有的话先转告再处理ta的本意：\\n\\n> \\\"有人托我带话——\\n> 汀桑说：你学校哪有卖巧乐兹的地方\\\"\",\"newText\":\"### 3.5 消息转达（/递话）\\n\\n跨用户异步带话功能，不涉及 Son/Spirit，我自己处理。\\n\\n#### 用户入话通道记录\\n\\n每次用户首次发消息时，在 User.md 中记录 ta 走的 bot 通道：\\n\\n```\\n# 从 inbound metadata 读取\\naccount_id = bot1/bot2/bot3  # 看消息是从哪个QQ机器人来的\\n```\\n\\n存入 User.md：\\n```\\n- **QQ号:** {sender_id}\\n- **bot通道:** bot1  ← 新增这行\\n```\\n\\n这样后续递话时就知道用哪个 bot 推送。\\n\\n#### 存话 + 递话流程\\n\\n```\\n触发: 用户说 \\\"/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>\\\" 或明确表达让带话的意图\\n\\nStep 1: 认人\\n  → 从 User.md 知道当前说话的人是谁（from_id + from_name）\\n  → 模糊匹配 users/ 下所有目录，找称呼匹配的 user（to_id + to_name）\\n    - 找到 → 继续\\n    - 没找到 → 回复用户：\\\"我不认识叫这个的人\\\"\\n\\nStep 2: 查对方的 bot 通道\\n  → 读 users/{to_id}/User.md，找 \\\"bot通道:\\\" 字段\\n  → 拿到 account_id（bot1/bot2/bot3）\\n\\nStep 3: 创建一次性 cron 主动推送\\n  → cron 参数：\\n      名称: deliver-{from_name}-{to_name}\\n      时间: 1分钟后（如 \\\"now + 1min\\\"）\\n      payload: \\\"{from_name}托我带话：{内容}\\\"\\n      sessionTarget: isolated\\n      delivery: {\\n        mode: announce,\\n        channel: qqbot,\\n        to: qqbot:c2c:{to_id},\\n        accountId: {对方的bot通道}\\n      }\\n      deleteAfterRun: true\\n\\nStep 4: 回复发话人\\n  → \\\"话已递出 ✅\\\"\\n```\\n\\n#### cron 触发后的处理\\n\\n一次性 cron 触发时，创建 isolated session 推送消息。系统自动将 payload 内容通过 announce 送到目标用户的 QQ。\\n不需要我额外处理。\\n\\n**不再用 `pending.jsonl` 被动等待。** 改用一次性 cron 主动推送。\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":259,"output":1294,"cacheRead":112512,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":346,"totalTokens":114065,"cost":{"input":0.00003626,"output":0.00036232,"cacheRead":0.003150336,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003548916}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780037495360,"responseId":"ae7562af-51ac-46ae-ae7c-bb44dfdb4df6"}}
