{"type":"message","id":"183303d1","parentId":"9b2129b8","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:52:15.622Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_GmOChELe0K5h73mTXFvj6301","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"f4ffeb12-5427-40c4-8172-88f5646eb4ce\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"deliver-汀桑-雾籽米\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780037424727,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"at\",\n        \"at\": \"2026-05-29T06:52:00.000Z\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"汀桑托我带话：你学校哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot2\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780037520000,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1780037520022\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780037424727\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"faye-dreaming\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1779984077157,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 6 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780092000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780005600020,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 201547,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780005801567\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 2,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 2,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"f4ffeb12-5427-40c4-8172-88f5646eb4ce\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> qqbot:c2c:346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    }\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"f4ffeb12-5427-40c4-8172-88f5646eb4ce","agentId":"father","name":"deliver-汀桑-雾籽米","enabled":true,"deleteAfterRun":true,"createdAtMs":1780037424727,"schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-05-29T06:52:00.000Z"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"汀桑托我带话：你学校哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀","timeoutSeconds":30},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D","accountId":"bot2"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780037520000,"runningAtMs":1780037520022},"updatedAtMs":1780037424727},{"id":"f37cede8-