{"type":"message","id":"3d25ae83","parentId":"d71272cc","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:54:20.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit has returned the menu content. Let me organize it nicely for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"📋 **已注册功能（共 4 个）**\n\n**1. 🍾 漂流瓶**\n`/扔瓶子` `/捞瓶子` `/看瓶子` `/回复瓶子`\n匿名扔消息，捞瓶子，一条龙\n\n**2. 📋 备忘录**\n`/记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录`\n记待办、查列表、切状态\n\n**3. 🌅 早朝官**\n`/早朝` `/设早朝 HH:MM` `/关早朝`\n每天自动推送待办+瓶子+童话+饮食+摄影建议\n\n**4. 📸 相册笔记**\n`/存照片` `/看相册` `/搜照片` `/删照片`\n存图加注释，标签搜索\n\n---\n\n顺便，刚才雾籽米那条消息走错了 bot（bot2 写的 bot3），你跟我说了之后我已经改成 bot3 了。雾籽米有回复你的话吗？没的话我重新用 bot3 推一次？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":114837,"output":238,"cacheRead":5504,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":17,"totalTokens":120579,"cost":{"input":0.01607718,"output":0.00006664,"cacheRead":0.000154112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016297932}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780037651874,"responseId":"6fd46bb6-c284-4400-adaf-f9b86a03da08"}}
