{"type":"message","id":"74e11265","parentId":"a5a05c8f","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:55:08.856Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to send a message to 雾籽米 asking where to find 巧乐兹 at their school. I need to use the new cron-based delivery approach.\n\nLet me check 雾籽米's User.md for the bot通道.\n\nI already updated it to bot3. Let me create the cron job.\n\nThe steps:\n1. from_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 (汀桑)\n2. to_id: 346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D (雾籽米)\n3. 雾籽米's bot channel: bot3\n4. Create a one-shot cron with announce delivery\n\nLet me set it to fire 1 minute from now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QhfrXiLxqPLMVdqEO6xt0008","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"deliver-汀桑-雾籽米","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-05-29T07:01:00.000Z"},"payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"汀桑托我带话：学校里哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀"},"sessionTarget":"main","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D","accountId":"bot3"},"deleteAfterRun":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\":\"deliver-汀桑-雾籽米\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"at\",\"at\":\"2026-05-29T07:01:00.000Z\"},\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"systemEvent\",\"text\":\"汀桑托我带话：学校里哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"main\",\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\",\"channel\":\"qqbot\",\"to\":\"qqbot:c2c:346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D\",\"accountId\":\"bot3\"},\"deleteAfterRun\":true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1705,"output":346,"cacheRead":118528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":165,"totalTokens":120579,"cost":{"input":0.00023870000000000003,"output":0.00009688000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003318784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036543640000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780037704728,"responseId":"5eed2721-c458-459e-8a2e-188c143f8977"}}
