{"type":"message","id":"9226f730","parentId":"ca3c18ca","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:55:12.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah, the cron's delivery mode announce is only supported for `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"`. So I need to use sessionTarget: \"isolated\" instead. For an isolated session, the payload should be `kind: \"agentTurn\"`, not `systemEvent`.\n\nLet me fix this - use agentTurn with isolated session.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_XyxQgMI00IN4AZCdIdFd2800","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"deliver-汀桑-雾籽米","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-05-29T07:01:00.000Z"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"汀桑托我带话：学校里哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀","timeoutSeconds":30},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D","accountId":"bot3"},"deleteAfterRun":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\":\"deliver-汀桑-雾籽米\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"at\",\"at\":\"2026-05-29T07:01:00.000Z\"},\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"汀桑托我带话：学校里哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀\",\"timeoutSeconds\":30},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\",\"channel\":\"qqbot\",\"to\":\"qqbot:c2c:346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D\",\"accountId\":\"bot3\"},\"deleteAfterRun\":true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":53,"output":257,"cacheRead":120576,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":69,"totalTokens":120886,"cost":{"input":0.00000742,"output":0.00007196000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003376128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003455508}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780037709539,"responseId":"1eccf7a1-0dbe-4d99-9f2d-a474dd47fc66"}}
