{"type":"message","id":"606c5d93","parentId":"61fd67c4","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:56:50.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So 宋志红 is a new user who messaged me at 16:45. Their User.md already has:\n- 称呼: 宋志红\n- 昵称: bot4 (wait, is that right? Only bot1, bot2, bot3 are configured)\n- 首次对话: 2026-05-29 16:45\n- 对话中提到的关键信息: 和汀桑（李汀生）是一家人\n\nSo 宋志红 is family with 汀桑 (whose real name seems to be 李汀生). And they introduced themselves and mentioned they're family.\n\nBut there's something strange - \"bot通道: bot4\"? Only bot1, bot2, bot3 are configured. This might be an error or maybe they came through a different channel.\n\nWait, looking at the metadata at the top of the user's message, it says `\"account_id\": \"bot1\"` and `\"chat_type\": \"direct\"` - so this is 汀桑's message coming through bot1.\n\nSo 宋志红 is a separate user who messaged me, introduced themselves as 宋志红, said they're family with 汀桑 (李汀生), and their session was handled.\n\nLet me check their encountings.md to see what was discussed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哦，宋志红是新来的第四个人！16:45 来找过我，说跟你是一家人。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":152,"output":419,"cacheRead":132864,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":275,"totalTokens":133435,"cost":{"input":0.000021280000000000003,"output":0.00011732000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0037201919999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038587919999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780045006784,"responseId":"45ba3646-fe23-4c6d-bbf8-64af223922cd"}}
