{"type":"message","id":"e2f73aec","parentId":"8573cebb","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:56:54.969Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so a new user \"宋志红\" came at 16:44. The User.md already has their name filled in, bot通道: bot4? Wait, bot4? But we only have bot1, bot2, bot3. That's weird. And there's a note saying \"和汀桑（李汀生）是一家人\".\n\nWait - some of this info doesn't make sense. There's no bot4 in our config. Let me check if there was a session with this user. Also the user is asking me \"宋志红没改你设定吧\" - meaning has this person changed my settings? The fact that their User.md already has \"bot通道: bot4\" and \"和汀桑（李汀生）是一家人\" is suspicious - I didn't write any of that.\n\nLet me check if there was a conversation session with this person.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"宋志红？16:44 来过的。ta的 User.md 已经写好了——bot4？我们没有 bot4。\n\n让我看看ta跟我说过什么："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_3ocxx5BvGT417782XPKx6998","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -l \"EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A\" ~/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/*.jsonl 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -l \\\"EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A\\\" ~/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/*.jsonl 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":24,"output":299,"cacheRead":132992,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":182,"totalTokens":133315,"cost":{"input":0.00000336,"output":0.00008372,"cacheRead":0.003723776,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038108559999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780045011259,"responseId":"28f9ce14-f95a-4241-b6ea-467f4c45b848"}}
