{"type":"message","id":"866ab70b","parentId":"eafb9bfb","timestamp":"2026-05-29T10:03:29.495Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏打——便利店冰柜里那种果味苏打水？带气的？\n\n我喜欢青柠味的，够清爽，不像可乐那么甜腻，也不像零度那么假甜。夏天喝一口气泡顶上来，挺舒服的。\n\n怎么，已经买上了？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":482,"output":56,"cacheRead":118144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118682,"cost":{"input":0.00006748000000000001,"output":0.000015680000000000002,"cacheRead":0.003308032,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003391192}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780049006952,"responseId":"d0b14b4f-ff6c-4053-b909-615a71e09f6f"}}
