{"type":"message","id":"c4aa38ee","parentId":"107c6e55","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:02:19.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"没有，宋志红自打16:44那轮聊完就没再来过了。\n\n她最后一句话是\"谢谢🙏\"，我说了\"客气啥，一家人不说两家话\"，然后就没下文了。\n\n怎么，想让我主动给ta递个话？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":923,"output":54,"cacheRead":125312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126289,"cost":{"input":0.00012922,"output":0.000015120000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0035087359999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003653076}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780059737156,"responseId":"4a03a8e2-8ffa-4791-8bd6-b9d44454c84d"}}
