{"type":"message","id":"2e436ac0","parentId":"e70600d6","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:23:12.515Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"验证过了，cron 成功触发了 isolated session，但是有个问题——**isolated session 里我读 pending_urges.md 后，没法直接推消息给你。**\n\n因为 isolated session 的 `delivery: mode=none`，我的回复不会送到你那边。要推消息，需要在 cron 里面主动创建一次性 announce cron。\n\n让我看看现在的 pending_urges.md 状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_reZhZJmDF7XszddWFfSl1432","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":132021,"output":142,"cacheRead":4096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136259,"cost":{"input":0.01848294,"output":0.000039760000000000006,"cacheRead":0.000114688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018637388}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780060985545,"responseId":"43a60ef8-1695-4563-8760-cb7f16918468"}}
