{"type":"message","id":"585db896","parentId":"84ff4072","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:23:16.764Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"还是 pending，说明 isolated session 里没成功推。问题很清楚了——isolated session 跑完就完了，没有能力创建新的 cron job。\n\n**正确的逻辑应该是：cron 内运行的我不负责推，而是返回判断结果，然后由 cron 调度系统决定要不要推。**\n\n但更直接的方案是：**不设 cron，由我（主 session）自己处理。**\n\n思路是这样的——AGENTS.md 的 3.5 写得对，但执行方式要调。正确的链路是：\n\n```\n1. 设一个 cron \"faye-pending-urges\"\n2. cron 触发时 payload 带着\"检查 pending_urges.md 并推送\"\n3. cron 用 announce 模式直接发到我的主 session\n4. 我收到后自己处理：读文件 → 判断 → 建一次性 cron 推 → 标记\n```\n\n跟早朝官一样——早朝 cron 也是发到我的 session 里我来处理的。\n\n让我改："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TiyQwQEjD7ET8p6jAEPU1027","name":"cron","arguments":{"jobId":"5bb4a074-d4fe-4d60-9ce0-53ac5aa629a8","action":"remove"},"partialArgs":"{\"jobId\": \"5bb4a074-d4fe-4d60-9ce0-53ac5aa629a8\", \"action\": \"remove\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":294,"output":289,"cacheRead":136192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136775,"cost":{"input":0.000041160000000000006,"output":0.00008092,"cacheRead":0.003813376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0039354559999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780060992964,"responseId":"156bab7e-b791-4b4f-928f-9164c0bf8f17"}}
