{"type":"message","id":"d5d27cb0","parentId":"e62371ce","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:23:49.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Wvw2KfoMcCqMYi5ZKngL1440","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":202,"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"limit\": 40, \"offset\": 202, \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":109,"output":87,"cacheRead":140160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140356,"cost":{"input":0.00001526,"output":0.00002436,"cacheRead":0.00392448,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0039641}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780061026800,"responseId":"1d3c7033-dc5f-4636-8f48-3de4a9db6f04"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4306b84","parentId":"d5d27cb0","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:23:49.378Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Wvw2KfoMcCqMYi5ZKngL1440","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 3.5 主动话题推送\n\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头，在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\n\n#### 数据来源\n\n`heart/pending_urges.md` — dreaming 5.5 步骤生成。\n\n#### 推送判断流程\n\n```\n触发: cron \"faye-pending-urges\" 每 6h 触发\n\nStep 1: 读 heart/pending_urges.md\n → 筛选 status=pending 的条目\n\nStep 2: 逐个判断\n → 检查 min_interval_hours 过了吗（从上一次推送到现在）\n → 检查对方今天有没有主动找我？（最近 12h 内说过话 → 不打扰）\n → 熟悉度 < 3/10 → 跳过（不熟的人别突然说话）\n\nStep 3: 满足条件 → 创建一次性 announce cron 推送\n → payload 直接用 urge 字段文本，不加前缀\n → delivery 按对方 bot 通道推送\n → 推完标记 status=delivered\n\nStep 4: 所有判断完，写回 pending_urges.md\n```\n\n#### 推送时的语气\n\n一次性 cron 推送时 payload 就是纯文本，自然地以 Faye 语气说话：\n\n> \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n\n不写\"这是系统消息\"，不写\"Faye说\"，就是 Faye 在说话。\n\n---\n\n### 3.6 消息转达（/递话）\n\n[319 more lines in file. Use offset=242 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780061029377}}
