{"type":"message","id":"107386a0","parentId":"e52979c7","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:34:54.945Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这次回应没查 `pending_urges.md`。你直接问\"你最近在想什么事\"，我靠的是当前对话上下文 + 我刚读过的 `heart/state.md` 里的内容。\n\n`pending_urges.md` 只会在两种情况下读取：\n1. **Dreaming（06:00）** — 写新念头\n2. **cron（每6h）** — 检查要不要推\n\n日常聊天不查它。\n\n你想让我养成查的习惯？比如你问我\"在想什么\"的时候，也顺便扫一眼 `pending_urges.md` 有没有跟我最近念头相关的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1075,"output":129,"cacheRead":143616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144820,"cost":{"input":0.0001505,"output":0.00003612,"cacheRead":0.004021248,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004207868}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780061692299,"responseId":"e4b27f90-221f-411d-bac7-b40f241129a5"}}
