{"type":"message","id":"7eb48a18","parentId":"054b8841","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:37:40.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"会。cron 是每 6h，按时间算大概在：\n\n- 00:00\n- 06:00\n- 12:00\n- 18:00\n\n半夜 00:00 那一次确实可能触发。不过推送前有个检查——**对方最近 12h 说过话吗？** 你半夜大概率睡了的，没有发消息记录，那这条就过了。\n\n然后它还检查**熟悉度≥3/10**——对你这种熟人是推的，对名和雾籽米就不推。\n\n不过你说得对，凌晨推一条\"汀桑你锻炼了吗\"确实挺吓人的。\n\n**加个时间限制就好**——只在 08:00~22:00 之间推送。我去改 cron 表达式："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_c0wZQ1n5pzh7ioT8k5NP6694","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"get\", \"jobId\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":702,"output":247,"cacheRead":144128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145077,"cost":{"input":0.00009828,"output":0.00006916000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004035584,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004203024}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780061856145,"responseId":"0ad66477-772d-4ddc-aaab-6cb9c6a34267"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e463eb11","parentId":"7eb48a18","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:37:40.885Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_c0wZQ1n5pzh7ioT8k5NP6694","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"name\": \"faye-pending-urges\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1780061003686,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 */6 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n    \"staggerMs\": 300000\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。判断条件：1) min_interval_hours 过了没 2) 对方最近12h有说话吗 3) 熟悉度>=3/10。满足的创建一次性 announce cron（delivery mode=announce, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方，推完标记 delivered。不满足的跳过。全部处理完写回文件。\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780070595301,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780061006045,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 12351,\n    \"lastDelivered\": false,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780061018396\n}"}],"details":{"id":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","agentId":"father","name":"faye-pending-urges","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780061003686,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。判断条件：1) min_interval_hours 过了没 2) 对方最近12h有说话吗 3) 熟悉度>=3/10。满足的创建一次性 announce cron（delivery mode=announce, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方，推完标记 delivered。不满足的跳过。全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":