{"type":"message","id":"983efac7","parentId":"1d6d03d2","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:37:47.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在 payload 里加了时间判断——**超过 22:00 就不推**。下次检查是下一个 6h 窗口。\n\n下次触发时间应该在凌晨 00:00 附近——到时候它会看到超过 22:00，跳过，等 06:00 再处理。\n\n这样你半夜不会被吵醒🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":476,"output":69,"cacheRead":145792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146337,"cost":{"input":0.00006664,"output":0.00001932,"cacheRead":0.004082176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004168136}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780061864757,"responseId":"c82304db-1783-4598-953a-18d93ab8baea"}}
{"type":"message","id":"18e15a1c","parentId":"983efac7","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:50:01.145Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"你一句别怂，我就敢往前冲😄张雪峰老师，我还记得你😫一句一句把我拉出迷雾里🥶张雪峰老师，我还记得你😘那些年少的愁，你替我扛起😍粉笔灰落在肩上，像雪一样安静🌬️你笑着说前途远，别先把自己看清😟多少个深夜回家，我还在翻那页纸你说过的每句话都在我心里记起后来风吹过来，我也学会了不躲不退，往自己的山坡走张雪峰老师，我还记得你😁一句一句把我拉出迷雾里😭张雪峰你替我扛起🤓如果有一天我走得很远🙂也会想起那间教室的光线🤨桌子旁，说别怕吃苦😇说这条路总会有人走出去","timestamp":1780062598108}}
{"type":"message","id":"1637fd80","parentId":"18e15a1c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:50:04.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哈？你这是被什么歌洗脑了还是自己在写词？\n\n张雪峰老师——那个考研段子手、报考指南专业户？你跟他有啥渊源，能写出这么长一段来😏\n\n不过说真的，\"粉笔灰落在肩上，像雪一样安静\"这句还挺好——不管是谁写的。怎么，最近翻到了以前记的东西？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2121,"output":76,"cacheRead":144384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146581,"cost":{"input":0.00029694000000000004,"output":0.000021280000000000003,"cacheRead":0.004042752,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004360972}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780062601208,"responseId":"d3fdb851-42f5-447f-a62a-511150bcdcf4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"481da470","parentId":"1637fd80","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:52:04.636Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"人类会享受搬💩的乐趣呢","timestamp":1780062723263}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2b9b600","parentId":"481da470","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:52:08.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哈？搬💩的乐趣？\n\n我寻思人类不会。但如果你说的是**那种**搬💩——比如做了一堆脏活累活，回头看堆成山了，反而有种\"妈的这堆东西都是我干的\"的成就感——那倒是有的。\n\n像你今天改配置、搭流程、注册功能、调递话，回头一看 Bebop 号上从 1 个用户变成 4 个、从漂流瓶搭到主动推送——这不就是搬💩搬出个花园么😏\n\n不过真正的💩还是算了。那玩意儿没人爱搬。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2084,"output":125,"cacheRead":144512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146721,"cost":{"input":0.00029176,"output":0.000035000000000000004,"cacheRead":0.004046336,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004373096}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780062724748,"responseId":"939871bb-8f7c-43e1-9073-57393ec64230"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cdc26da","parentId":"d2b9b600","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:53:41.932Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"[Image]\nUser text:\n[qqbot 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 Fri 2026-05-29 21:53 GMT+8]\nDescription:\n这是一段以赛博朋克风格讽刺计算机专业现状的中文文字。文中将AI比作“义体”，暗示程序员过度依赖AI工具，如同赛博格般增强能力。所有人必须使用AI（义体）才能在竞争中生存，否则会被淘汰。装上“义体”后效率倍增，公司因此裁员。进入大公司可免费使用顶级AI，但离职后便失去支持。长期依赖导致人类丧失独立编码与代码审查能力，最终因提交大量bug引发严重事故，沦为“赛博疯子”。结尾感叹“真特么赛博朋克啊”，以黑色幽默揭示技术异化与职场困境。整体语言简洁，带有强烈讽刺与荒诞感。","timestamp":1780062820525,"MediaPath":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/CB9A8E6889ABBF8087308B58710E8F9B_1780062813108_218111.jpg","MediaPaths":["/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/CB9A8E6889ABBF8087308B58710E8F9B_1780062813108_218111.jpg"],"MediaType":"image/jpeg","MediaTypes":["image/jpeg"]}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"[media attached: /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/CB9A8E6889ABBF8087308B58710E8F9B_1780062813108_218111.jpg (image/jpeg)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Absolute and ~ paths only work when they stay inside your allowed file-read boundary; host file:// URLs are blocked. Keep caption in the text body.\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[qqbot 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 Fri 2026-05-29 21:53 GMT+8]\nDescription:\n这是一段以赛博朋克风格讽刺计算机专业现状的中文文字。文中将AI比作“义体”，暗示程序员过度依赖AI工具，如同赛博格般增强能力。所有人必须使用AI（义体）才能在竞争中生存，否则会被淘汰。装上“义体”后效率倍增，公司因此裁员。进入大公司可免费使用顶级AI，但离职后便失去支持。长期依赖导致人类丧失独立编码与代码审查能力，最终因提交大量bug引发严重事故，沦为“赛博疯子”。结尾感叹“真特么赛博朋克啊”，以黑色幽默揭示技术异化与职场困境。整体语言简洁，带有强烈讽刺与荒诞感。","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"551821cd","parentId":"6cdc26da","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:53:41.933Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"174ec820","parentId":"551821cd","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:53:44.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vZ2BzVmyAFHwOMDh3VGh6980","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/CB9A8E6889ABBF8087308B58710E8F9B_1780062813108_218111.jpg","prompt":"请完整读出图片中的所有文字内容"},"partialArgs":"{\"image\": \"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/CB9A8E6889ABBF8087308B58710E8F9B_1780062813108_218111.jpg\", \"prompt\": \"请完整读出图片中的所有文字内容\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1256,"output":107,"cacheRead":146048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147411,"cost":{"input":0.00017584000000000002,"output":0.00002996,"cacheRead":0.004089344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004295144}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780062821972,"responseId":"7cfea00b-6855-47e0-a79f-05860ac9b72d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"eaada8e1","parentId":"174ec820","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:53:49.626Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_vZ2BzVmyAFHwOMDh3VGh6980","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"cs专业已经活在赛博朋克⁺了，ai就是义体\n\n所有人都必须要买义体，否则你卷不过装了义体的人\n\n装了义体之后，一个人可以顶十个人，于是公司计划开掉一半人\n\n进了大公司可以免费用上顶级义体，但是离开大公司就没得用了\n\nai用多了，开始失去写代码、review代码的能力，然后在某一天commit了一堆bug引发t0事故⁺（化身赛博疯子）\n\n真特么赛博朋克啊"}],"details":{"model":"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest","image":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/CB9A8E6889ABBF8087308B58710E8F9B_1780062813108_218111.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780062829625}}
{"type":"message","id":"5978a9ad","parentId":"eaada8e1","timestamp":"2026-05-29T13:53:52.951Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这段写得挺真的。AI 是义体这个比喻绝了——装上就强，不装就被淘汰，装久了发现自己已经不会\"原生\"写代码了。\n\n你现在就在船尾跟我这个义体聊天，算不算已经装了一半了😏\n\n不过说实话——你搭我这套三位一体，不是把代码全丢给 AI 然后自己不会写了。你是在设计架构、搭流程、让我帮你做 executor 的活。这是\"义体用得明白\"的那种人，不是被义体反噬的那种。\n\n最后那句\"真特么赛博朋克啊\"——配你刚发的那个张雪峰歌词，感觉你今天是个 poet night🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":204,"output":141,"cacheRead":147328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147673,"cost":{"input":0.00002856,"output":0.00003948,"cacheRead":0.004125184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004193224}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780062829659,"responseId":"fa0d8711-daf8-4a9f-abdd-693a1c923a48"}}
