{"type":"message","id":"d189515a","parentId":"3b7b1ee7","timestamp":"2026-05-29T14:30:20.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📸 已存 1 张照片！\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nID: ALB-20260529-0012\n注释: \"半夜出来逛华侨城\"\n标签: #出行\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n查看全部: /看相册\n\n半夜逛华侨城挺有氛围的——那个走廊照片是你拍的吧？确实挺有那种空荡荡的工业感🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":52,"output":92,"cacheRead":151552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151696,"cost":{"input":0.000007280000000000001,"output":0.00002576,"cacheRead":0.004243456,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004276495999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780065017803,"responseId":"8f7a82a6-bf34-4b60-8b3a-59fbd9a0b17a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"efda0dd5","parentId":"d189515a","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:29:19.645Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"- Voice: /root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/20260529232913_85d4500d050c493da3a0b878b8ca470b_1780068555232_ed5e1d.wav, https://qqbot.ugcimg.cn/uservoice/20260529232913_85d4500d050c493da3a0b878b8ca470b.wav\n- ASR: 你知不知道跟芒果树有关的情歌，英文或者中文？\n\n[Voice message] 你知不知道跟芒果树有关的情歌，英文或者中文？","timestamp":1780068556749}}
{"type":"message","id":"936cbbc8","parentId":"efda0dd5","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:29:25.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"芒果树有关的情歌……让我想想🍧\n\n中文的话最有名的是**《Mango》——胡琳**，不过那是首粤语的，挺冷门。\n\n英文的话：\n- **《Mango Tree》——Angus & Julia Stone**（澳洲民谣，很温柔）\n- **《Mango》——Bibio**（电子民谣，暖暖的）\n- **《Under the Mango Tree》——传统牙买加民谣**（牙买加情歌，很多版本，最著名的是1962年James Bond电影《Dr. No》里唱的版本）\n\n不过说实话，**最合适的可能是《Mango Tree》Angus & Julia Stone**——歌词是关于sitting under a mango tree, waiting for love, 节奏轻松，适合半夜听。\n\n你怎么想起芒果树了——你们学校路边有芒果树？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2462,"output":180,"cacheRead":149248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151890,"cost":{"input":0.00034468000000000004,"output":0.000050400000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0041789439999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0045740239999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780068559701,"responseId":"8c062a93-39d8-4efa-a1e3-6be4a87e585a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"23832802","parentId":"936cbbc8","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:44:44.617Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"[Image]\nUser text:\n[qqbot 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 Fri 2026-05-29 23:44 GMT+8]\nDescription:\nThe image captures a cozy, intimate live music performance at \"Penny Black Club,\" as indicated by the circular logo on the blue backdrop. The stage is lit with soft lighting, featuring a jazz or fusion band with musicians playing guitar, saxophone, upright bass, and drums. In the foreground, patrons sit at small wooden tables surrounded by greenery, enjoying drinks and the ambiance. A large leaf from a plant partially frames the left side of the scene, adding to the relaxed, garden-like atmosphe","timestamp":1780069482273,"MediaPath":"/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/B7761B5165CC97EC63FD5B8A0E8FB8E2_1780069472431_cf68a1.jpg","MediaPaths":["/root/.openclaw/media/qqbot/downloads/B7761B5165CC97EC63FD5B8A0E8FB8E2_1780069472431_cf68a1.jpg"],"MediaType":"image/jpeg","MediaTypes":["image/jpeg"]}}
