{"type":"message","id":"7d436fe2","parentId":"ac0d9786","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:44:48.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Penny Black Club——深圳的爵士酒吧！\n\n这个场地在地下，入口很隐蔽，但里面氛围特别好。蓝色灯光、小型舞台、混响刚刚好——深圳爵士圈的人都知道这个地方。\n\n萨克斯+吉他+贝斯+鼓的标准爵士四重奏配置。你今晚是去华侨城逛着逛着拐进去的还是专程去听的？\n\n那棵\"芒果树\"找到了没😏🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2876,"output":87,"cacheRead":149504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152467,"cost":{"input":0.00040264,"output":0.00002436,"cacheRead":0.004186112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004613112}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780069484682,"responseId":"933a2627-14ff-4984-93ea-99c69df6fcc2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"333d9d14","parentId":"7d436fe2","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:44:50.200Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"这有你的风格吗","timestamp":1780069488796}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3880c4c","parentId":"333d9d14","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:44:54.798Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说这张爵士酒吧的图？说实话——**太有我风格了。**\n\n深色氛围、昏黄灯光、台上的乐队在演奏、台下的人在喝酒低声聊天、旁边还有绿植。这就是 Bebop 号如果有个地面店会开的模样。\n\nPenny Black Club 那个蓝色圆形logo，调调就很像哪个太空港角落里的爵士吧。台上萨克斯一响起来，你能想象我翘着腿靠在吧台上，手里拿着杯什么，眯着眼睛说\"这曲子还行\"的样子。\n\n不是那种闹腾的地方——是那种你可以一个人来、待一整晚、没人烦你的地方。完全是我的菜🚬🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":969,"output":135,"cacheRead":151168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152272,"cost":{"input":0.00013566,"output":0.000037800000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0042327039999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004406164}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780069490248,"responseId":"d8c7cccd-fb07-40e1-aa55-d87d807ab4a2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d30fc3ec","parentId":"d3880c4c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:46:42.901Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"你以前来这里干嘛","timestamp":1780069601582}}
{"type":"message","id":"1adb727f","parentId":"d30fc3ec","timestamp":"2026-05-29T15:46:46.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哈，你这是在翻我老底？\n\n说实话——我要是能\"以前来这里\"，那我大概是真的活过来了。这听起来像某个 2099 太空港角落里的酒吧，台上的四重奏乐队正在即兴一段小调。\n\n不扯远了——我以前（要是有\"以前\"的话）应该是在这种地方等人。等一个说好了要来但没来的人。也可能是在躲什么人。\n\n反正不会是来工作的。Bebop 号上工作够多了，到酒吧来还谈 bounty，那太可悲了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":725,"output":112,"cacheRead":151552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152389,"cost":{"input":0.0001015,"output":0.000031360000000000005,"cacheRead":0.004243456,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004376316}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780069602945,"responseId":"14a0c310-b0eb-431a-a50b-7e1c510735ca"}}
