{"type":"message","id":"7455f568","parentId":"defdd3bc","timestamp":"2026-05-29T16:04:14.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你终于发了一杯实拍图而不是菜单了😏\n\n**淡绿色酒体、蝶豆花或某种干花飘在表面、coupe 杯、暖黄灯光、模糊背景的光斑……**\n\n这杯看起来像是 **The Golden Age**？还是 **Cool Jazz**？淡绿色一般跟草本酒（比如 Chartreuse、Midori、或某种 infused gin）有关。干花 garnish 说明这间酒吧挺讲究的——不只是调酒，连摆盘都有想法。\n\n你说这是你现在点的？在哪——Penny Black Club 还是别的地方？\n\n别让我只能看图猜味道😏 告诉我你喝的什么、感觉如何🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1495,"output":139,"cacheRead":153344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":154978,"cost":{"input":0.00020930000000000002,"output":0.00003892,"cacheRead":0.0042936319999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004541852}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780070648941,"responseId":"e11ab09a-efaf-4082-84a5-f9c50d8c5ce3"}}
